1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,840
Only two people could’ve
done it! You or Mother Müzeyyen!

2
00:00:07,160 --> 00:00:09,640
Don’t you ever try to
play games like this again!

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,680
If we’re siblings, then
we should be together.

4
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:18,120
From now on, I want Burak to
live with us at the mansion.

5
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:21,120
Mercan and Ateş are the ones hurting me.

6
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:23,440
Don't worry, I know.

7
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,240
The photo in the study.

8
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,440
You put it there.

9
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,520
You’re doing the wrong thing, Aslı.

10
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,720
They’re together now. They love each other.

11
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:33,640
Everything I do, I do for love.

12
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:38,080
What are you doing
here? Get out of my house!

13
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,320
Burak…

14
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:42,240
come in, son. This is your home too.

15
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:45,480
This is my home and my
children’s home, Haydar Effendi!

16
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:49,640
If he’s part of this family,
he should live here too.

17
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:52,920
Since when you are the one
making decisions in this house?

18
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,880
Mercan is the lady of this house.

19
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,960
She has every right to make decisions.

20
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:05,000
Ateş Karahan secretly had Tahir
Aslan’s parents’ graves opened.

21
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,640
Spent a fortune to keep it quiet.

22
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,720
Is Ateş Karahan… Tahir Aslan?!

23
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:14,640
This is my first and last
kindness to you, Mercan.

24
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,640
Since you want the truth,

25
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,800
if you trust your love so much,

26
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:25,240
take this key and look in the basement.

27
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:30,760
"Play on her mercy, her pure heart."

28
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:37,840
"To break her from her family,
exposing Haydar’s dirt is enough."

29
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:44,360
"If the family turns on each
other, they’re easier to destroy."

30
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,560
What?

31
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:53,880
