38
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,200
Open settings.

39
00:02:12,201 --> 00:02:14,719
Choose Audio Track and pick your language.

40
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:18,000
The full Audio track upload
schedule is in the description below.

41
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:30,040
Really… Is this really you, Tahir?

42
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,280
Tahir?

43
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,480
Tahir?

44
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,360
Is this really you?

45
00:03:55,840 --> 00:04:03,840
You… Who are you? What kind
of game are you playing with me?

46
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:13,200
A game… It was not a
game. It was not a game.

47
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,640
I truly am Tahir.

48
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:25,680
I looked for you. I thought you were dead.

49
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:29,560
I was devastated… Tahir…

50
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:39,840
I… I searched for you.
They told me you were dead.

51
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,440
They told me you had died.

52
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:50,480
You know I was looking for Tahir.

53
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:56,600
We looked together. We
went to Eylül’s grave.

54
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,320
My God, protect my sanity.

55
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,720
Why… Why… Tell me why?

56
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:19,720
Why so many lies? Say it… Say it, come on,
say it. Do not stay silent, say something.

57
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,720
Why are you silent? Say something.

58
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:41,120
I… I could not say it.

59
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,840
I could not.

60
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,360
I was unable to.

61
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:58,600
Why… Why did you do all this?

62
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:04,200
Why did you do it? Why?

63
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,920
Tell me, come on.

64
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:22,320
These photos, these documents,
these files, why are they here?

65
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:26,800
What are these? Why… Why are they here?

66
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:33,840
What is all this? Why are they here?

67
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,920
Do not just stand there in
silence, get up and say something.

68
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,920
Do not stay silent.

69
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,679
Why you played so many games,

70
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:54,520
why you hid your identity and
married me, tell me already.

71
00:06:55,400 --> 00:07:01,560
This means you have been
watching us for a long time.

72
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,680
What are these? Why are they here?

73
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,840
What are these?

74
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,640
Why are they here?

75
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:19,480
So you have been watching
us for a long time, huh?

76
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:23,039
Or did you plan everything?

77
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,279
Murat’s debt,

78
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:27,399
what happened to me,

79
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:30,960
all this suffering I endured for so long.

80
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:05,120
You… You scratched out his face.

81
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:14,280
Please… Come on.

82
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:21,480
Look… You have no part in Murat’s, my
brother’s, my brother’s death, right Ateş?

83
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,160
Please tell me no.

84
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:28,440
Say I did not know, say
I knew nothing, please.

85
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:32,400
Say I knew nothing too…

86
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,599
I…

87
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:47,480
I did not want him to die.

88
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:15,000
You, the man I loved, the man I
fell for, could not have done this.

89
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:23,000
He could not. This is impossible.

90
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:26,480
I cannot be this wrong about you.

91
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:30,560
Talk to me. Say something.

92
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:35,120
Tell me this is a dream, that
I am trapped in a nightmare.

93
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:38,440
Say none of this is real,
say there is no revenge.

94
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,880
Tell me you are not Tahir.

95
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,400
Look, if you say it, I will believe you.

96
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,320
Tell me you are not Tahir.

97
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,560
Come on.

98
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:54,800
Do not stay silent. Talk.
I said do not stay silent.

99
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,680
Why are you silent?

100
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:05,080
But you… You said you loved me.

101
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,400
You said you loved me deeply.

102
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,560
I was your precious pearl, Mercan.

103
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,080
Was all of it a lie?

104
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,920
Was all of it a game?

105
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:26,040
When you said my love, the
voice rising from your heart…

106
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:31,920
the compassion, mercy, love in your eyes
when you looked at me, was all of it a lie?

107
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:42,360
When you touched my face, that trembling
in your hand, afraid of hurting me…

108
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:47,040
Was all of it part of your revenge?

109
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,360
Was all of it a lie?

110
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,560
Was it all a lie, say it.

111
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,360
No.

112
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,800
No.

113
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,440
None of it was.

114
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,200
All of it was real.

115
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:07,840
How was I so foolish?

116
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,640
How did I fail to see anything?

117
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:17,280
You… How did you become so cruel, Ateş?

118
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:28,760
Sorry, or should I call you Tahir?

119
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:55,040
Did you enjoy playing
with my feelings at least?

120
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,800
Did I entertain you?

121
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,200
What did you think?

122
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,120
What did you say behind my back?

123
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,920
How did you mock me?

124
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:10,240
You must have said how stupid she
is, how easily she believed, right?

125
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:11,920
You are right.

126
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,440
One must be foolish.

127
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:17,400
One must be foolish, you are right.

128
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,960
I came for revenge, yes.

129
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,280
Yes.

130
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,680
But I fell in love with you, Mercan.

131
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,880
Madly.

132
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:38,080
Do not. Do not touch me.

133
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:42,080
Let that last touch stay with me.

134
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,880
At least do not steal that from me.

135
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,960
I truly loved you, Mercan.

136
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,880
I never wanted to hurt you.

137
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:23,120
Stop… What love are you talking about?

138
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:26,160
There is no love inside so many lies.

139
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,000
Do you hear me?

140
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,400
There is no love.

141
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:35,880
You are a liar.

142
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,600
A liar.

143
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,560
Mercan? My daughter, what happened?

144
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:12,760
Mercan.

145
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,680
Haydar.

146
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:35,680
Mercan came from the storage
room like she saw a ghost.

147
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,200
Clearly something is there.

148
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,640
What do you mean something is there?

149
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:40,840
I do not know.

150
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:43,480
These people are not letting us go in.

151
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:52,920
Cemal.

152
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,160
Stop. It is too late now.

153
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:08,160
What is going on here?

154
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,800
Why are they near the storage room?

155
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,680
Aslı.

156
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:35,480
Mercan. We need to talk.

157
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,880
Open the door.

158
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,440
Mercan.

159
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,240
Mercan.

160
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:46,800
Mercan, please open the door.

161
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:47,840
We need to talk.

162
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:56,280
Mercan.

163
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,480
Are you okay, Mercan?

164
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,280
Open the door.

165
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:01,840
If you do not, I will break it.

166
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,560
Mercan, let me explain.

167
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,680
Listen once.

168
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:09,080
I know you are in shock. So am I.

169
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,680
I could not tell you the truth.

170
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:11,880
But please listen.

171
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:13,920
Go away.

172
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:18,280
Leave me alone.

173
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:20,400
I do not even want to see your face.

174
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:31,080
Mercan, please do not stay silent.

175
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,480
Scream, rage, get angry,
but do not stay silent.

176
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:52,160
Fine.

177
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,040
Then I will stay here
until you open the door.

178
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:44,320
These are photos from years ago.

179
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:49,480
Everything was in front
of us. How did we miss it?

180
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:53,080
All of this is my fault.

181
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:56,960
Panic blinded me.

182
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,240
The blame is mine.

183
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,520
Is he really Tahir?

184
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,320
Yes.

185
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,040
Tahir.

186
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:13,480
No way. How is this possible?

187
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:16,040
He was a poor orphan.

188
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:20,320
How did he gain such
wealth at such a young age?

189
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,080
I do not know, Nermin.

190
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:27,240
All I know is we are
inside a massive scheme.

191
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:29,520
My head…

192
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,200
He planned everything.

193
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,320
He did everything.

194
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:36,240
And I swallowed it all.

195
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,520
They had my son killed.

196
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:49,240
They dragged him into this pit.

197
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:53,160
Look, they have been watching us for years.

198
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:04,360
If not for you, my son would be alive.

199
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:06,080
Nermin, stop.

200
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:10,720
Who are you?

201
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,320
Why are you with Tahir?

202
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:16,440
Why do you hate me and my family? Speak.

203
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,960
Do you remember Ahmet?

204
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:30,480
Ahmet Taner.

205
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:38,680
I am sure you remember.

206
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,120
Ahmet was my husband.

207
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,720
You killed him.

208
00:19:52,120 --> 00:19:53,560
What nonsense are you talking about?

209
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:55,320
I killed no one.

210
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,800
I did not kill Ahmet or your husband.

211
00:19:58,840 --> 00:20:00,079
Ahmet was filth.

212
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:03,680
One of the men he ruined probably
killed him and dumped him somewhere.

213
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:09,480
You liar. You deny it shamelessly?

214
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:14,040
You did not only kill my
husband, you killed my baby.

215
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,720
What baby?

216
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:23,280
What are you talking about?

217
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:28,040
When I heard about Ahmet,
I gave birth at home.

218
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,000
My baby died without me ever smelling him.

219
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:33,320
I barely even saw him.

220
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:38,640
Tahir and you are chasing
revenge at the wrong door.

221
00:20:39,560 --> 00:20:40,800
You knocked on the wrong door.

222
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:42,760
You nursed hatred for nothing.

223
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,040
I did not kill your husband.

224
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:51,800
I am here to turn your life
into hell, Haydar Yıldırım.

225
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,560
You already did.

226
00:21:00,840 --> 00:21:03,280
You had my son killed in return
for your son’s blood price.

227
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:03,720
Nermin.

228
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,319
You are my son’s murderer.

229
00:21:05,320 --> 00:21:07,120
You will answer for this.

230
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:14,760
Will I ask you?

231
00:21:15,760 --> 00:21:17,240
This is a family matter.

232
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,920
It does not concern you.

233
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,600
What are you doing here anyway?

234
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,680
I am here for your mother’s health, Berat.

235
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:32,080
I said my family’s
health does not concern you.

236
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,680
Do you not understand? Go.

237
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:34,880
Brother. What?

238
00:21:34,881 --> 00:21:42,640
Brother, will you fight
at a time like this?

239
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:45,280
Malik, please go.

240
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,800
We will talk later.

241
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,160
Fine.

242
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:50,120
Call me if you need anything.

243
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:51,280
Fine.

244
00:21:52,120 --> 00:21:53,120
My God, listen to them.

245
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:54,440
My mother.

246
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,360
Mother, are you okay?

247
00:21:58,560 --> 00:22:00,240
Look, your son is happy.

248
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:01,320
Be happy too.

249
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,480
Look.

250
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:09,399
He married the woman he loves.

251
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,920
He built a home.

252
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:12,760
Mother.
Well done.

253
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:17,800
Are you mocking us?

254
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:20,240
The woman almost collapsed
and you talk about marriage.

255
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:22,280
Stay out of this, Çiçek.

256
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:26,640
Mother, you were almost
having a heart attack.

257
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,999
Çiçek, listen…

258
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,560
Why do you still pour fuel on the fire?

259
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:30,600
I am leaving then.
Yes.

260
00:22:31,320 --> 00:22:32,720
This one meddles, that one meddles.

261
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,359
We stayed out and saw the result.

262
00:22:36,360 --> 00:22:39,520
You married the first
girl you met, huh Berat?

263
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,160
Bravo.

264
00:22:41,320 --> 00:22:42,360
Bravo, my son.

265
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:44,280
What am I here?

266
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:46,639
Who am I here? What am I?

267
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,200
What am I? Who am I?

268
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:50,800
Bravo to you.

269
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:52,120
Bravo to you too.

270
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:53,400
Bravo, my girl.

271
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:57,760
So my anchovy brained
son went and married you.

272
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,560
Why did you not say anything, my girl?

273
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:02,800
Why did you rush like
smuggling goods out of a fire?

274
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,959
You said yes right away and married him.

275
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:06,560
Why, my girl? Why?

276
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,840
We were going to tell you.

277
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:10,320
We truly were.

278
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,439
When were you going to tell me?

279
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,080
Mother…

280
00:23:12,081 --> 00:23:16,600
When? You wore the dress,
the ring is on, you married.

281
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:21,400
So you married, huh?

282
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:22,400
Yes.

283
00:23:23,120 --> 00:23:24,120
Çiçek.

284
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,679
Çiçek, for God’s sake hold me.

285
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,720
Hold my hand or there will be trouble.

286
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,160
My girl.

287
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,719
You did not even bother to ask my consent.

288
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,720
Who am I, for God’s sake?

289
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:35,920
Am I nothing?

290
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:37,680
Berat, tell me.

291
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:40,520
Mother, how could that be?

292
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,000
How could it?

293
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:43,320
You are my only one.

294
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:45,360
How could it… It happened.

295
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,200
What happened happened.

296
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,640
Mother…
What happened happened.

297
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,800
Mother, calm down.

298
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:50,080
Come.

299
00:23:50,081 --> 00:23:52,079
Bring cologne, my girl.

300
00:23:52,080 --> 00:23:53,320
Okay.

301
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:56,120
Mother, not too much.

302
00:23:57,520 --> 00:23:59,000
My God, help us.

303
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,800
Berat…

304
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,520
May God deal with you, Berat.

305
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,040
Where shall I go now?

306
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:09,960
You…

307
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:11,920
Since you did not count me…

308
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:14,560
Since you did not treat me like a person…

309
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,200
I am telling you both.

310
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,400
I do not count you either.

311
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:19,600
Done.

312
00:24:19,760 --> 00:24:21,080
Go, wherever you go.

313
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,160
Take your wife and go.

314
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:53,320
Mercan, we must talk.

315
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,880
Open the door.

316
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:07,200
I wanted to explain for a long time.

317
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:11,080
I could not.

318
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:16,240
I feared you pulling away.

319
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,960
I could not risk losing you.

320
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:23,840
You are right.

321
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,440
You should have heard it from me first.

322
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:40,520
I love you, Mercan.

323
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:43,600
I am madly in love with you.

324
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,040
I never lied about this.

325
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:49,640
I tried to tell you, you stopped me.

326
00:25:57,280 --> 00:25:59,040
Never again…

327
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:01,200
Never say you love me.

328
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:07,520
I do not want to hear this lie again.

329
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:13,280
If you loved me, you would not stop.

330
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:16,800
Everything except my love was a lie.

331
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:22,760
But you were my only truth.

332
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,760
You lit a fire inside me.

333
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:29,840
Do not touch me. Let go.

334
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,320
Your hand is bleeding.

335
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:35,480
I said let go.

336
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,640
I cannot leave you like this.

337
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:39,840
I will not. Do you hear me?

338
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:44,160
Come inside.

339
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,920
She was Ahmet’s wife.

340
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:25,120
Oh Haydar.

341
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,240
What have you done?

342
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,360
How did you let these
people into your home?

343
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,480
Is what she says true?

344
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:39,240
Do not talk nonsense, Nermin.

345
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:40,560
The woman is ill.

346
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:43,520
I am losing my mind.

347
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:46,120
So they came for revenge.

348
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:51,839
Tahir…

349
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:56,120
That woman called Müzeyyen
turned our lives into a nightmare.

350
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:00,160
She had our son killed.

351
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:03,280
Who knows what else she will do?

352
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,880
You are responsible for all this, Haydar.

353
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:08,520
You are right.

354
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:11,000
Because of me.

355
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:18,200
I should have suspected
Müzeyyen’s meaningless hatred.

356
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:28,360
What now?

357
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:31,280
Everyone is tense.

358
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:35,120
Oh Nezir, do not ask.

359
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:37,680
If only you knew what happened.

360
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:43,120
We learned who Ateş is.

361
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:32,720
I am sorry.

362
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:34,560
For everything.

363
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,800
For hurting you…

364
00:29:42,280 --> 00:29:45,240
For lying.

365
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,320
Please do not stay silent, Mercan.

366
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:01,280
Scream, rage, but do not stay silent.

367
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:06,920
Why?

368
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,200
Why did you hide your identity?

369
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,879
What revenge are you taking on us?

370
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,920
What did we do to you?

371
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:15,680
What did I do?

372
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:21,200
What do you want from me?

373
00:30:26,320 --> 00:30:27,120
Talk.

374
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:29,360
Answer me.

375
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,440
Why 187 days?

376
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:33,880
What is this 187 days?

377
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:42,520
If you have no answer, why talk?

378
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,079
Take it.

379
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:57,080
All of it is yours.

380
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,000
All of it.

381
00:30:59,880 --> 00:31:01,440
All of it and your lies.

382
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,159
I cannot grasp this.

383
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,960
How can a person lie so much?

384
00:31:11,080 --> 00:31:12,240
How does one do this?

385
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:16,640
How?

386
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,200
You are right.

387
00:31:24,600 --> 00:31:25,760
Completely right.

388
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,680
Please give me time.

389
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,680
I…

390
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:43,000
I will explain everything.

391
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:48,640
I have no time for you.

392
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,240
Do you hear me?

393
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,120
No…

394
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:05,280
You did not only take the man I loved…

395
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:07,840
You took my childhood.

396
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,320
How do you do this?

397
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:27,240
How can I trust someone
capable of such schemes?

398
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,480
I do not trust you.

399
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:30,280
My brother would never hurt my mother.

400
00:33:30,560 --> 00:33:31,400
That vile witch…

401
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:33,560
She poisoned my brother’s mind.

402
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:36,239
Çiçek, you are angry.

403
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:38,400
But think.

404
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:41,559
If Berat did not want to marry Zehra…

405
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:43,120
she could not convince him.

406
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,000
They married willingly.

407
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:47,440
No, Malik, I disagree.

408
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:52,400
That girl manipulates my brother.

409
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:55,440
We must save him.

410
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:58,279
Look, my love…

411
00:33:58,280 --> 00:34:00,640
We do not know their feelings.

412
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,200
Judging is wrong.

413
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:04,120
Maybe Zehra changed.

414
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,760
Maybe she loves Berat…

415
00:34:07,960 --> 00:34:09,120
Like he loves her.

416
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:11,720
You cannot believe this.

417
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:14,920
She loves no one but herself.

418
00:34:15,240 --> 00:34:17,600
Even love serves her interest.

419
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,760
Think again.

420
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:22,280
What interest could Zehra have?

421
00:34:22,640 --> 00:34:24,160
Money? No.

422
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,599
Working at the mansion?

423
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,640
No, she already works there.

424
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,760
See?

425
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:34,239
Am I the only one seeing her true face?

426
00:34:34,240 --> 00:34:37,120
Something is wrong with her nature.

427
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,400
This marriage must end.

428
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,439
Çiçek…

429
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,040
I know heartbreak.

430
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:48,319
When I thought of losing you…

431
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,800
my world collapsed.

432
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:51,839
So…

433
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,399
if they love each other…

434
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,680
we should not interfere.

435
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,680
MALIK ARABIC 01

436
00:34:57,240 --> 00:34:59,479
Meaning…

437
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,839
bearing sin is wrong.

438
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,880
No.

439
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:04,960
This marriage will not last.

440
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:06,800
Zehra will bring trouble.

441
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,200
I am telling you.

442
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,000
No way.

443
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:24,840
I asked you many times
who Ateş Karahan was.

444
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:29,120
You lied, Aslı.

445
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:32,680
I could not tell you who Ateş was.

446
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,760
Ateş would have killed me.

447
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:39,920
I broke Mercan and Ateş apart.

448
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,040
What more do you want?

449
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:44,520
You will pay for wasting my time.

450
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:48,080
What are you accusing me of?

451
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,480
I did not win alone.

452
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,520
You won too.

453
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:57,280
Without me you would not enter the company.

454
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:03,240
Ateş missed the clause thanks to me.

455
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:09,880
Yet you accuse me.

456
