466
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,280
Are you listening to us?

467
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,920
Me?

468
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:03,720
No.

469
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:05,920
Come here.

470
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:26,640
I just arrived.

471
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:28,399
But when you say us…

472
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,800
Listen, Burak.

473
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,120
You wander too much.

474
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:33,920
Stop.

475
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,080
We will talk later.

476
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,000
What is it to you?

477
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,520
This is my mansion.

478
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,760
I go where I want.

479
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:56,040
Here or there.

480
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,320
He ruined everything.

481
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:03,440
Thank God my hand hurts…

482
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,880
Tahir.

483
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:40,560
So everything was your plan.

484
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:43,600
You are a menace.

485
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:46,520
How dare you enter my family?

486
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:12,680
I am not the Tahir you locked away.

487
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:16,079
Once more…

488
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:19,120
If you raise your hand again…

489
00:39:20,120 --> 00:39:21,520
I swear I will break it.

490
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,640
What do you want?

491
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:29,000
What is your plan?

492
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:30,040
To kill me?

493
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:31,920
No.

494
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,600
I have no such intent.

495
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:37,400
Death would be salvation for you.

496
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:42,320
I will not grant it.

497
00:39:43,720 --> 00:39:44,440
You…

498
00:39:44,441 --> 00:39:46,880
You will beg me to die.

499
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,759
You stole my childhood.

500
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:58,200
You stole my family.

501
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,040
You stole my sister.

502
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:07,119
Not only my past…

503
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:09,600
my future too.

504
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,880
Did you think I would let this go?

505
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,680
You lost your mind.

506
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:18,519
This hatred will ruin…

507
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:19,920
Mercan’s life too.

508
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,400
Do not say Mercan’s name.

509
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,960
I have nothing to lose.

510
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:33,440
Except her.

511
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:05,480
Çiçek, bring hot water.

512
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:06,680
Okay.

513
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,560
Wow.

514
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,560
So Ateş Bey is Tahir?

515
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:17,560
Yes. He is our Tahir.

516
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:21,040
How did I not recognize him?

517
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,840
Oh my dear.

518
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,320
He grew into a man.

519
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:26,839
I understand nothing.

520
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,960
Why did he change his name?

521
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:33,800
Who is he anyway?

522
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,480
Did you know?

523
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:45,000
No.

524
00:41:46,040 --> 00:41:47,360
I knew nothing.

525
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:53,040
I swear I knew nothing.

526
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,720
I heard the name Tahir for the first time.

527
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:02,080
He has a score with the family.

528
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:09,960
I vaguely remember Tahir.

529
00:42:14,200 --> 00:42:16,640
His sadness makes sense now.

530
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:19,760
Tahir was a good child.

531
00:42:20,560 --> 00:42:21,960
I loved him.

532
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:23,440
Oh my dear.

533
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:25,240
Does he stay here?

534
00:42:27,120 --> 00:42:28,520
He became a strong young man.

535
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:32,520
It showed since childhood.

536
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:34,640
Oh my dear.

537
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:40,000
When things calm down, I will talk to him.

538
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:43,280
But chaos will grow.

539
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:45,240
It will not settle.

540
00:42:46,080 --> 00:42:48,080
What did Mercan do?

541
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,680
This is awful.

542
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:52,840
You love a man.

543
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:54,760
Then he becomes someone else.

544
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,920
Awful.

545
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:06,800
I will wash the lentils.

546
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:10,320
Çiçek, turn off the stove.

547
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,400
Just in case.

548
00:43:25,080 --> 00:43:28,600
You know something, do not you?

549
00:43:32,600 --> 00:43:35,840
You eavesdrop.

550
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:37,880
Çiçek.

551
00:43:42,360 --> 00:43:43,440
Speak honestly.

552
00:43:48,800 --> 00:43:49,800
Sister in law?

553
00:43:50,160 --> 00:43:51,160
Yes.

554
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,280
She is your sister in law.

555
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:56,960
Patience.

556
00:44:20,480 --> 00:44:21,480
Look.

557
00:44:21,800 --> 00:44:22,920
You scolded me for nothing.

558
00:44:23,560 --> 00:44:25,480
Chaos is good.

559
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:28,840
Mercan’s world collapsed.

560
00:44:32,480 --> 00:44:34,240
Why do you not listen to me?

561
00:44:34,680 --> 00:44:36,600
Why do you create problems?

562
00:44:37,680 --> 00:44:40,240
If I did not speak, Ateş would.

563
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:45,439
Good thing I did.

564
00:44:45,440 --> 00:44:48,360
Their bond will never heal.

565
00:44:48,720 --> 00:44:50,600
You know nothing, Aslı.

566
00:44:55,600 --> 00:44:56,880
What do I not know?

567
00:45:07,240 --> 00:45:08,760
How did Mercan enter the storage room?

568
00:45:09,960 --> 00:45:10,960
How?

569
00:45:12,120 --> 00:45:13,120
She did.

570
00:45:14,960 --> 00:45:16,000
How would I know?

571
00:45:16,640 --> 00:45:19,559
Using it was wrong from the start.

572
00:45:19,560 --> 00:45:21,520
Someone would see.

573
00:45:22,200 --> 00:45:23,200
You are lying.

574
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:26,840
What are you accusing me of?

575
00:45:28,760 --> 00:45:30,680
You were going to tell everything.

576
00:45:31,680 --> 00:45:33,080
She should not learn this way.

577
00:45:33,480 --> 00:45:35,040
I should have told her.

578
00:45:36,920 --> 00:45:38,280
I know what you did.

579
00:45:39,080 --> 00:45:40,600
I did not.

580
00:45:41,400 --> 00:45:42,880
She went in herself.

581
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:49,040
Why do you care so much?

582
00:45:49,920 --> 00:45:54,600
If she truly loves you, she will not leave.

583
00:46:08,280 --> 00:46:10,120
I cannot believe you.

584
00:46:13,920 --> 00:46:15,240
Despite everything…

585
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:19,320
I was so wrong trusting you.

586
00:47:00,960 --> 00:47:01,960
Look at this.

587
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:03,240
Everything spills out.

588
00:47:04,040 --> 00:47:06,000
One should care for their home.

589
00:47:06,400 --> 00:47:08,039
Three salaries enter this house.

590
00:47:08,040 --> 00:47:11,920
They hoard money.

591
00:47:12,200 --> 00:47:15,080
Fine, I know how to spend it.

592
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,600
Furniture must change first.

593
00:47:26,960 --> 00:47:28,840
Enjoy your meal, my wife.

594
00:47:30,520 --> 00:47:31,520
Thanks.

595
00:47:33,840 --> 00:47:35,160
Did you rest?

596
00:47:35,880 --> 00:47:36,880
A little.

597
00:47:38,680 --> 00:47:39,680
Berat.
Yes?

598
00:47:42,320 --> 00:47:45,840
We married today and started work.

599
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:50,720
We obey orders, right?

600
00:47:53,080 --> 00:47:54,400
No honeymoon.

601
00:47:55,720 --> 00:47:57,360
We married suddenly.

602
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:59,160
When would we go?

603
00:48:03,680 --> 00:48:05,280
Where will we sleep?

604
00:48:06,080 --> 00:48:07,080
In my room.

605
00:48:07,920 --> 00:48:10,040
Do not be ridiculous.

606
00:48:10,280 --> 00:48:11,280
The bed is small.

607
00:48:12,600 --> 00:48:15,480
We squeeze.

608
00:48:16,520 --> 00:48:17,640
No.

609
00:48:18,200 --> 00:48:19,560
We must shop.

610
00:48:20,200 --> 00:48:22,320
A new bride arrived.

611
00:48:28,520 --> 00:48:30,280
I will not stay there.

612
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:32,920
Too small.

613
00:48:33,160 --> 00:48:34,320
No space for my things.

614
00:48:36,680 --> 00:48:38,240
Which room will you not stay in?

615
00:48:39,120 --> 00:48:41,160
Berat’s tiny room.

616
00:48:43,560 --> 00:48:47,400
You think this is a palace?

617
00:48:47,840 --> 00:48:48,520
Remember.

618
00:48:48,720 --> 00:48:51,280
This is the annex.

619
00:48:52,800 --> 00:48:56,440
God forbid.

620
00:49:32,480 --> 00:49:34,600
I love him.

621
00:49:36,120 --> 00:49:37,120
Understand.

622
00:50:20,440 --> 00:50:22,159
I want nothing.

623
00:50:22,160 --> 00:50:26,280
I do not want to see or speak.

624
00:50:28,400 --> 00:50:29,520
Mercan, please.

625
00:50:29,840 --> 00:50:30,880
Let me stay near you.

626
00:50:37,120 --> 00:50:38,200
As who?

627
00:50:38,760 --> 00:50:39,760
Who are you?

628
00:50:40,240 --> 00:50:41,960
I do not even know.

629
00:50:43,080 --> 00:50:45,080
Why enter as Ateş?

630
00:50:45,320 --> 00:50:46,320
I know nothing.

631
00:50:47,280 --> 00:50:49,000
I will be whoever you want.

632
00:50:49,840 --> 00:50:51,120
Just do not leave.

633
00:50:55,160 --> 00:50:57,160
You will never forgive me, right?

634
00:50:58,960 --> 00:51:01,240
Would you forgive?

635
00:51:02,600 --> 00:51:03,600
Was it worth it?

636
00:51:04,040 --> 00:51:05,480
All this pain?

637
00:51:05,520 --> 00:51:07,440
All the suffering you caused?

638
00:51:08,040 --> 00:51:11,400
My brother died because of ambition.

639
00:51:14,080 --> 00:51:15,520
There are things you do not know.

640
00:51:16,440 --> 00:51:19,439
I never wanted harm.

641
00:51:19,440 --> 00:51:21,320
Then what?

642
00:51:21,960 --> 00:51:22,960
Tell everything.

643
00:51:23,760 --> 00:51:25,120
No. I do not want.

644
00:51:25,880 --> 00:51:26,880
Do not explain.

645
00:51:27,600 --> 00:51:29,440
I do not care why.

646
00:51:30,560 --> 00:51:33,240
After destruction, what meaning remains?

647
00:51:35,280 --> 00:51:37,320
I trusted you.

648
00:51:46,240 --> 00:51:50,560
Trust again. Listen.

649
00:51:54,240 --> 00:51:54,560
Let go.

650
00:51:55,120 --> 00:51:55,680
I will not.

651
00:51:55,840 --> 00:51:56,880
Let go.

652
00:51:57,360 --> 00:51:59,920
You played with my feelings.

653
00:52:00,520 --> 00:52:02,000
I opened my heart.

654
00:52:03,200 --> 00:52:05,920
You were my first and last.

655
00:52:10,320 --> 00:52:12,640
Not worth it.

656
00:52:15,200 --> 00:52:16,200
Worth it.

657
00:52:23,440 --> 00:52:24,800
Our bond is worth everything.

658
00:53:05,000 --> 00:53:07,880
You were my first and last.

659
00:53:17,600 --> 00:53:19,680
My girl, what are you doing?

660
00:53:20,200 --> 00:53:22,720
This is the kitchen.

661
00:53:25,320 --> 00:53:27,200
Why do you not help?

662
00:53:29,160 --> 00:53:31,600
I married today.

663
00:53:31,760 --> 00:53:33,320
Expecting work is rude.

664
00:53:38,160 --> 00:53:39,960
Today is my day off.

665
00:53:40,360 --> 00:53:41,720
No one can make me work.

666
00:53:47,640 --> 00:53:49,320
I need to shop.

667
00:54:01,920 --> 00:54:03,360
Shame.

668
00:54:03,400 --> 00:54:06,440
Will you ruin our home?

669
00:54:06,600 --> 00:54:08,560
What prices are these?

670
00:54:09,840 --> 00:54:10,920
I am a new bride.

671
00:54:11,640 --> 00:54:13,440
I will get what I want.

672
00:54:14,120 --> 00:54:16,200
My husband circles around me.

673
00:54:16,480 --> 00:54:17,480
He handles it.

674
00:54:24,440 --> 00:54:25,880
I am tired of sitting.

675
00:54:28,200 --> 00:54:32,200
I will rest at home.

676
00:54:33,640 --> 00:54:36,360
You forgot you serve Müzeyyen Hanım.

677
00:54:44,000 --> 00:54:46,680
She will devour my brother.

678
00:55:19,480 --> 00:55:20,640
I love him.

679
00:55:22,440 --> 00:55:24,560
Deeply.

680
00:55:26,760 --> 00:55:27,959
You are Ateş.

681
00:55:27,960 --> 00:55:29,960
I am drawn to fire.

682
00:55:32,320 --> 00:55:36,200
Lies surrounded me.

683
00:55:37,200 --> 00:55:39,840
You freed me.

684
00:55:40,800 --> 00:55:43,680
You gave me hope.

685
00:55:48,360 --> 00:55:51,520
One more blow and I fall.

686
00:56:12,800 --> 00:56:14,080
I knew this.

687
00:56:20,880 --> 00:56:23,280
She will not look at me.

688
00:56:27,840 --> 00:56:29,000
I lost Mercan.

689
00:56:36,160 --> 00:56:37,480
I would explain.

690
00:56:40,280 --> 00:56:42,200
Aslı and Müzeyyen stopped me.

691
00:56:47,160 --> 00:56:50,640
However she learned…

692
00:56:51,160 --> 00:56:54,039
I cannot accept forgiving Haydar.

693
00:56:54,040 --> 00:57:00,239
Your suffering, your sister…

694
00:57:00,240 --> 00:57:02,440
She cannot ignore this.

695
00:57:02,600 --> 00:57:04,640
Something is wrong.

696
00:57:07,040 --> 00:57:08,400
I told her nothing.

697
00:57:14,760 --> 00:57:16,760
After all that destruction…

698
00:57:17,240 --> 00:57:19,240
I could not tell her about her father.

699
00:57:24,840 --> 00:57:26,680
Better she knows nothing now.

700
00:57:28,160 --> 00:57:30,400
What shall I say?

701
00:57:31,680 --> 00:57:35,360
Is her distance not natural?

702
00:57:36,480 --> 00:57:38,640
Put yourself in her place.

703
00:57:40,560 --> 00:57:42,440
She is devastated.

704
00:57:43,760 --> 00:57:45,680
She loves you.

705
00:57:46,560 --> 00:57:48,080
You miss my point.

706
00:57:48,240 --> 00:57:49,400
Let me repeat.

707
00:57:50,240 --> 00:57:51,840
She loves you.

708
00:57:56,520 --> 00:57:58,720
You searched for Tahir together.

709
00:57:59,840 --> 00:58:00,879
What more do you want?

710
00:58:00,880 --> 00:58:03,080
She deserves truth.

711
00:58:09,120 --> 00:58:10,120
I do not know.

712
00:58:11,480 --> 00:58:12,640
I am lost.

713
00:58:19,160 --> 00:58:23,400
I sharpened myself with revenge.

714
00:58:26,200 --> 00:58:28,760
I earned money for revenge.

715
00:58:35,720 --> 00:58:37,760
Müzeyyen fueled it.

716
00:58:41,040 --> 00:58:42,040
Fate.

717
00:58:48,720 --> 00:58:51,200
I fell for Haydar’s daughter.

718
00:58:52,720 --> 00:58:54,920
I feel trapped.

719
00:59:01,200 --> 00:59:02,960
I cannot give her up.

720
00:59:03,760 --> 00:59:04,960
I cannot.

721
00:59:09,480 --> 00:59:10,480
Ateş, listen.

722
00:59:11,360 --> 00:59:12,600
You say it yourself.

723
00:59:12,840 --> 00:59:14,760
You must talk to her.

724
00:59:16,960 --> 00:59:19,960
Truth is her right.

725
00:59:20,720 --> 00:59:21,440
I understand you.

726
00:59:21,720 --> 00:59:22,960
You feel stuck.

727
00:59:23,920 --> 00:59:26,960
Only way out is talking.

728
00:59:28,680 --> 00:59:32,320
Or you may lose her forever.

729
00:59:44,600 --> 00:59:46,400
You took not only the man I loved…

730
00:59:47,400 --> 00:59:48,960
you took my childhood.

731
00:59:57,800 --> 00:59:59,519
What did Mercan Hanım do?

732
00:59:59,520 --> 01:00:02,440
I worry.

733
01:00:03,280 --> 01:00:04,280
Strange, right?

734
01:00:05,640 --> 01:00:06,960
Yes.

735
01:00:09,200 --> 01:00:11,040
I am exhausted.

736
01:00:12,000 --> 01:00:13,160
You are right.

737
01:00:13,400 --> 01:00:15,999
With your mother’s work…

738
01:00:16,000 --> 01:00:17,680
you tired.

739
01:00:17,840 --> 01:00:18,840
I feel for you.

740
01:00:19,160 --> 01:00:21,679
Work is not the issue…

741
01:00:21,680 --> 01:00:23,200
unrest drained me.

742
01:00:24,560 --> 01:00:25,840
Zehra moved in.

743
01:00:26,560 --> 01:00:28,360
Seeing her angers me.

744
01:00:33,320 --> 01:00:34,320
Çiçek.

745
01:00:37,400 --> 01:00:39,960
I must tell you something.

746
01:00:41,640 --> 01:00:42,640
What happened?

747
01:00:44,000 --> 01:00:46,399
As I said…

748
01:00:46,400 --> 01:00:48,520
I want no secrets.

749
01:00:54,920 --> 01:00:57,320
My family planned a future in Egypt.

750
01:00:58,280 --> 01:00:59,639
They want me back.

751
01:00:59,640 --> 01:01:01,040
To run companies.

752
01:01:01,560 --> 01:01:03,280
To marry chosen bride.

753
01:01:07,240 --> 01:01:09,240
They will not approve us?

754
01:01:13,080 --> 01:01:13,760
Meaning…

755
01:01:13,761 --> 01:01:16,200
They approve no one unwanted.

756
01:01:16,480 --> 01:01:18,679
Especially someone tying me to Istanbul…

757
01:01:18,680 --> 01:01:19,680
never.

758
01:01:25,760 --> 01:01:27,320
My father has not spoken for two years.

759
01:01:31,360 --> 01:01:34,240
I left everything for you.

760
01:01:36,600 --> 01:01:37,080
Çiçek.

761
01:01:37,081 --> 01:01:40,200
From now on…

762
01:01:41,400 --> 01:01:43,120
our road is hard.

763
01:01:46,640 --> 01:01:48,520
My love…

764
01:01:52,000 --> 01:01:54,080
strong enough.

765
01:01:57,000 --> 01:01:58,800
Will you hold my hand…

766
01:01:59,960 --> 01:02:00,960
stay beside me…

767
01:02:03,520 --> 01:02:05,920
face everything with me?

768
01:02:12,120 --> 01:02:13,120
Always.

769
01:02:19,600 --> 01:02:21,040
I love you.

770
01:02:21,840 --> 01:02:22,840
I love you too.

771
01:02:45,200 --> 01:02:46,720
I would speak with Ateş Bey.

772
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:54,000
Speak to me.

773
01:02:55,920 --> 01:02:57,800
It is important.

774
01:02:59,320 --> 01:03:01,199
Ateş is not in mood.

775
01:03:01,200 --> 01:03:03,200
Speak to me.

776
01:03:03,320 --> 01:03:04,320
Same difference.

777
01:03:05,640 --> 01:03:09,240
I will speak. Take this seriously.

778
01:03:12,720 --> 01:03:13,720
Can I use this?

779
01:03:33,760 --> 01:03:34,999
This contract…

780
01:03:35,000 --> 01:03:36,400
Partnership with Nezir.

781
01:03:37,520 --> 01:03:39,520
I never noticed this clause.

782
01:03:43,520 --> 01:03:45,720
We can remove Nezir.

783
01:03:47,960 --> 01:03:49,280
How did Aslı miss this?

784
01:03:50,680 --> 01:03:52,680
She did not.

785
01:03:52,920 --> 01:03:53,920
She hid it.

786
01:03:54,560 --> 01:03:57,280
I overheard them.

787
01:03:58,560 --> 01:04:02,080
Aslı is the reason.

788
01:04:13,440 --> 01:04:15,360
Do not tell anyone yet.

789
01:04:16,280 --> 01:04:18,360
I will investigate.

790
01:04:19,600 --> 01:04:21,400
Okay.

791
01:04:21,520 --> 01:04:22,520
As you wish.

792
01:05:33,360 --> 01:05:34,640
Will you ignore me?

793
01:05:43,920 --> 01:05:46,200
I disappointed you.

794
01:06:00,960 --> 01:06:02,440
What do you want from me?

795
01:06:04,760 --> 01:06:06,040
What is your aim?

796
01:06:07,920 --> 01:06:10,120
You lied for months.

797
01:06:11,640 --> 01:06:14,240
You made my family suffer.

798
01:06:19,040 --> 01:06:20,880
You expect forgiveness?

799
01:06:22,120 --> 01:06:25,240
How can I forgive?

800
01:06:31,040 --> 01:06:33,560
We lived hell here.

801
01:06:34,920 --> 01:06:39,200
I fought hatred for weeks.

802
01:06:40,480 --> 01:06:41,919
My brother…

803
01:06:41,920 --> 01:06:43,600
died.

804
01:06:44,240 --> 01:06:45,800
Müzeyyen caused it.

805
01:06:47,720 --> 01:06:49,159
Listen to me.

806
01:06:49,160 --> 01:06:50,560
You listen.

807
01:06:53,320 --> 01:06:56,040
I trusted you despite everything.

808
01:06:57,680 --> 01:06:59,760
I did not run with Nezir.

809
01:06:59,880 --> 01:07:00,880
I stayed.

810
01:07:03,640 --> 01:07:05,280
Why did you make me love you?

811
01:07:06,840 --> 01:07:08,400
What did you want?

812
01:07:08,880 --> 01:07:10,880
What did I do?

813
01:07:11,640 --> 01:07:14,360
You hurt my family.

814
01:07:15,680 --> 01:07:18,480
What revenge is this?

815
01:07:18,600 --> 01:07:19,720
What did we do?

816
01:07:20,080 --> 01:07:21,080
Why the name Ateş?

817
01:07:21,280 --> 01:07:23,240
Why 187 days of marriage?

818
01:07:23,760 --> 01:07:28,680
187 days we were locked in basement.

819
01:07:36,480 --> 01:07:39,680
Exactly 187 days.

820
01:07:40,440 --> 01:07:44,040
Your father tortured us.

821
01:07:52,800 --> 01:07:56,880
Darkness, hunger, cold.

822
01:08:07,240 --> 01:08:09,480
He imprisoned us.

823
01:08:16,880 --> 01:08:17,880
While you were safe…

824
01:08:20,480 --> 01:08:22,920
we fought to survive.

825
01:08:29,440 --> 01:08:32,480
You only saw me in garden.

826
01:08:40,360 --> 01:08:41,720
Did you see me otherwise?

827
01:08:48,920 --> 01:08:50,560
Your father gave us hell.

828
01:08:54,520 --> 01:08:56,240
Without reason.

829
01:08:59,920 --> 01:09:04,559
You sought revenge for this?

830
01:09:04,560 --> 01:09:07,200
Was this it?

831
01:09:09,800 --> 01:09:12,360
I wish it were.

832
01:09:15,600 --> 01:09:17,799
I am not someone…

833
01:09:17,800 --> 01:09:22,320
seeking revenge for hunger alone.

834
01:09:25,560 --> 01:09:27,840
You saw my scars.

835
01:09:32,280 --> 01:09:33,479
Then why Ateş?

836
01:09:33,480 --> 01:09:36,040
Why all this?

837
01:09:48,960 --> 01:09:50,080
My sister…

838
01:09:59,840 --> 01:10:01,560
Eylül…

839
01:10:10,720 --> 01:10:11,840
Your father…

840
01:10:16,280 --> 01:10:17,880
my sister…

841
01:10:19,320 --> 01:10:21,400
killed Eylül.

842
01:10:22,680 --> 01:10:24,119
He killed Eylül.

843
01:10:24,120 --> 01:10:25,720
My sister…

844
01:10:26,160 --> 01:10:27,479
He killed Eylül.

845
01:10:27,480 --> 01:10:29,560
Your father killed my…

846
01:11:18,640 --> 01:11:19,880
Your father…

847
01:11:24,560 --> 01:11:26,200
my sibling…

848
01:11:27,600 --> 01:11:29,280
killed Eylül.

849
01:11:30,840 --> 01:11:31,880
He killed Eylül.

850
01:11:32,440 --> 01:11:33,840
My sibling…

851
01:11:34,560 --> 01:11:35,560
he killed Eylül.

852
01:11:35,720 --> 01:11:38,120
Your father killed my sibling…

853
01:12:08,520 --> 01:12:12,479
No, no, no…

854
01:12:12,480 --> 01:12:14,719
No, my father is not a man this cruel.

855
01:12:14,720 --> 01:12:16,320
He would never do such a thing.

856
01:12:17,000 --> 01:12:20,880
You, you are lying. You
are a first rate liar.

857
01:12:21,240 --> 01:12:24,200
You are saying all this to hurt me, right?

858
01:12:24,720 --> 01:12:27,680
The last thing I would ever
want is to hurt you, Mercan.

859
01:12:32,240 --> 01:12:37,480
I wish none of this had happened.
I wish you had never suffered.

860
01:12:38,640 --> 01:12:41,520
Then what do you want from
me? Why are you doing this?

861
01:12:44,680 --> 01:12:48,560
Believe me, it is all
real. None of it is a lie.

862
01:12:54,160 --> 01:12:56,520
Believe me, seeing you like this breaks me.

863
01:12:58,320 --> 01:12:59,680
But this is the truth, Mercan.

864
01:13:01,920 --> 01:13:05,279
Stop it. Do not pretend
to feel sorry for me.

865
01:13:05,280 --> 01:13:07,160
Do not pretend to love me either.

866
01:13:07,760 --> 01:13:11,240
I know. All of this is part of your
revenge, part of your plan, right?

867
01:13:11,400 --> 01:13:14,800
Me too. That fake love
as well. All of it, right?

868
01:13:21,720 --> 01:13:23,680
Then say it. Say my
father did not kill Eylül.

869
01:13:24,880 --> 01:13:26,840
Believe me, what I am saying is not a lie.

870
01:13:28,160 --> 01:13:30,040
I wish none of this had ever happened.

871
01:13:31,040 --> 01:13:33,321
Even if you do not believe
it, this is the truth, Mercan.

872
01:13:34,920 --> 01:13:36,519
I know what I went through.

873
01:13:36,520 --> 01:13:38,760
I know what my sibling went through.

874
01:13:45,040 --> 01:13:46,759
I wish he had never done it.

875
01:13:46,760 --> 01:13:48,880
I wish Eylül were alive right now.

876
01:13:51,560 --> 01:13:54,760
But Eylül could not
endure that torment, Mercan.

877
01:13:58,880 --> 01:14:03,160
I watched her losing her
life day by day before my eyes.

878
01:14:06,760 --> 01:14:08,919
Every night when I close my eyes,

879
01:14:08,920 --> 01:14:15,040
that basement he turned into a prison
for us for 187 days comes back to me.

880
01:14:26,440 --> 01:14:27,960
I see him torturing Eylül.

881
01:14:29,440 --> 01:14:31,240
I see myself failing to protect my sibling.

882
01:14:41,960 --> 01:14:46,560
I could not protect my sibling.
I could not protect my sibling.

883
01:14:53,480 --> 01:14:56,439
I do not know how I am
alive while she is dead.

884
01:14:56,440 --> 01:14:59,120
I do not know how I am breathing, Mercan.

885
01:15:03,240 --> 01:15:05,960
I hate myself for being alive.

886
01:15:09,800 --> 01:15:12,040
I keep thinking I wish I
had died instead of her.

887
01:15:19,600 --> 01:15:22,519
That is the man you call your father.

888
01:15:22,520 --> 01:15:29,560
He made us suffer pain beyond words.

889
01:15:33,800 --> 01:15:36,360
Pain that will never fade.

890
01:15:39,120 --> 01:15:46,200
Years pass, yet I am still burning inside.

891
01:15:46,960 --> 01:15:52,240
That is why I named myself
Ateş. To become fire and burn.

892
01:16:20,240 --> 01:16:25,720
But I never knew I would light that
fire in your heart, Mercan. I never knew.

893
01:16:36,320 --> 01:16:37,800
Eylül...

894
01:16:42,240 --> 01:16:43,559
Eylül.

895
01:16:43,560 --> 01:16:51,360
No, no. I cannot be the
daughter of such a cruel man. No.

896
01:17:04,600 --> 01:17:12,520
You might be his daughter.
But you are not like him.

897
01:17:18,040 --> 01:17:19,960
You are not responsible for what he did.

898
01:17:21,920 --> 01:17:24,159
I do not know anymore.

899
01:17:24,160 --> 01:17:28,480
I do not know what to
believe, who to trust.

900
01:17:30,160 --> 01:17:33,839
My God, what are we being punished for?

901
01:17:33,840 --> 01:17:36,080
What are we living through?

902
01:17:46,880 --> 01:17:49,959
Another day is over.
How many days has it been?

903
01:17:49,960 --> 01:17:52,360
It has been 187 days, Eylül.

904
01:17:53,800 --> 01:17:57,960
When it becomes 200, you will save
me from here, right? You promised.

905
01:17:59,240 --> 01:18:01,039
Let my sister go. Let her go.

906
01:18:01,040 --> 01:18:02,040
I said let her go.

907
01:18:02,600 --> 01:18:03,600
Step back.

908
01:18:06,040 --> 01:18:08,480
She is dead. She is dead. You
will never ask about her again.

909
01:18:09,040 --> 01:18:11,801
Do you understand? You will do
exactly what I say. Speak up, damn it.

910
01:18:14,920 --> 01:18:18,200
Your mother and father are dead.
From now on, this is where you belong.

911
01:18:19,200 --> 01:18:20,200
Brother.

912
01:18:20,840 --> 01:18:21,840
I told you to move away.

913
01:19:13,880 --> 01:19:17,760
Your father killed my sibling, Eylül.

914
01:19:59,240 --> 01:20:02,399
We are finished. We are
finished, Haydar. Ruined.

915
01:20:02,400 --> 01:20:04,760
You heard what that woman said, right?

916
01:20:05,640 --> 01:20:06,920
She has completely lost control.

917
01:20:07,520 --> 01:20:11,839
Enough, Nermin. Stop hovering over me,
you are making my head spin. Sit down.

918
01:20:11,840 --> 01:20:15,039
That woman has sworn revenge.

919
01:20:15,040 --> 01:20:17,800
She might come after our lives
and you are telling me to sit.

920
01:20:21,400 --> 01:20:23,160
How are you this calm, Haydar?

921
01:20:24,760 --> 01:20:29,000
Who says I am calm, Nermin?
Do you think I know what to do?

922
01:20:33,040 --> 01:20:34,800
They have cornered us badly.

923
01:20:37,320 --> 01:20:39,359
This is all because of you.

924
01:20:39,360 --> 01:20:42,880
We are in this mess because of
the sins you committed in the past.

925
01:20:48,240 --> 01:20:52,560
That woman took revenge for what
you did to her son on my Murat.

926
01:20:53,520 --> 01:20:55,360
Because of you, I buried my son.

927
01:20:58,600 --> 01:21:03,359
Now it is our turn. You are responsible
for everything that has happened to us.

928
01:21:03,360 --> 01:21:07,999
Enough. Enough. Murat already…

929
01:21:08,000 --> 01:21:10,560
What? Murat already what?

930
01:21:12,520 --> 01:21:13,520
Nothing.

931
01:21:15,440 --> 01:21:17,759
There is nothing to defend
about what you did, right?

932
01:21:17,760 --> 01:21:19,120
That is why you are silent.

933
01:21:20,440 --> 01:21:21,480
Stop standing there.

934
01:21:22,800 --> 01:21:26,800
Do something before it is too
late. Clean up this mess. Save us.

935
01:21:42,520 --> 01:21:45,280
I swear I missed you so
much today, more than usual.

936
01:21:59,640 --> 01:22:01,360
Someone might see us.

937
01:22:02,400 --> 01:22:05,200
What happened? Did someone come?

938
01:22:05,400 --> 01:22:10,279
No, no. No one came but…

939
01:22:10,280 --> 01:22:14,440
The days when you will not worry about
being seen are very close. Very close.

940
01:22:15,200 --> 01:22:18,560
Yes, but until those days
come, we need to be careful.

941
01:22:19,800 --> 01:22:22,519
My mother has not recovered
from the shock my brother caused.

942
01:22:22,520 --> 01:22:24,520
I do not want her to see us.

943
01:22:25,880 --> 01:22:27,880
I am so afraid something
will happen to her.

944
01:22:28,880 --> 01:22:30,360
You are right, my love.

945
01:22:31,440 --> 01:22:33,679
Your Aunt Binnaz has fragile health.

946
01:22:33,680 --> 01:22:36,960
And I saw how upset
you get when she is ill.

947
01:22:39,200 --> 01:22:41,880
I cannot bear to see you upset.

948
01:22:43,520 --> 01:22:50,160
That is why whenever you want,
however you want, it will be that way.

949
01:22:51,680 --> 01:22:54,240
That is why I love you so much.

950
01:22:55,120 --> 01:22:58,319
Because you are like this,
because you are understanding…

951
01:22:58,320 --> 01:23:01,799
Because you look out not only
for me but also for my family.

952
01:23:01,800 --> 01:23:04,560
I feel very lucky.

953
01:23:05,360 --> 01:23:06,440
That luck is mine, my love.

954
01:23:08,880 --> 01:23:11,279
I love you so much…

955
01:23:11,280 --> 01:23:14,239
God truly loves me…

956
01:23:14,240 --> 01:23:17,520
that He put someone like
you in my path. I am so happy.

957
01:23:18,760 --> 01:23:20,440
Being like this feels so good.

958
01:23:21,680 --> 01:23:22,680
Like what?

959
01:23:23,000 --> 01:23:25,280
Like in the old days.

960
01:23:30,280 --> 01:23:31,840
The truly beautiful one is you.

961
01:23:44,400 --> 01:23:49,400
My parents are waiting
for me now. I need to go.

962
01:23:51,200 --> 01:23:55,360
All right then, you are leaving.

963
01:23:56,720 --> 01:23:57,720
Good night.

964
01:23:58,280 --> 01:24:00,680
Good night. See you tomorrow.

965
01:24:00,760 --> 01:24:01,760
See you.

966
01:24:11,920 --> 01:24:12,920
Dad.

967
01:24:13,480 --> 01:24:14,480
Yes, my daughter?

968
01:24:14,760 --> 01:24:17,040
My daughter? My daughter, huh?

969
01:24:19,120 --> 01:24:20,120
What about Eylül?

970
01:24:22,840 --> 01:24:23,560
Her…

971
01:24:23,561 --> 01:24:25,120
Did you kill her…

972
01:24:25,800 --> 01:24:27,640
My daughter, what is
wrong? What is happening?

973
01:24:30,320 --> 01:24:31,400
What are you trying to say?

974
01:24:33,200 --> 01:24:35,679
I cannot comprehend it anymore. I cannot.

975
01:24:35,680 --> 01:24:39,319
I do not know what to do.
I do not want to believe it.

976
01:24:39,320 --> 01:24:44,320
The man I called father, the man I relied
on my whole life, cannot have done this.

977
01:24:44,880 --> 01:24:47,760
My daughter, what are you saying?
What did I do to whom, for God’s sake?

978
01:24:49,040 --> 01:24:50,640
What did you do to Tahir and Eylül, dad?

979
01:24:55,560 --> 01:24:58,240
Did you really lock those
children in that basement?

980
01:24:59,520 --> 01:25:01,360
Eylül…

981
01:25:07,760 --> 01:25:10,600
Tell me it is not true.
Please tell me it is not true.

982
01:25:11,000 --> 01:25:13,320
Tell me you did not harm
that little girl. Please.

983
01:25:14,280 --> 01:25:17,120
That man called Ateş told
you all this, did he not?

984
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:19,879
He poisoned your mind.

985
01:25:19,880 --> 01:25:22,880
Are you going to believe a man
you met yesterday, or your father?

986
01:25:23,600 --> 01:25:26,560
That poor girl died of natural
causes on the way to the hospital.

987
01:25:27,720 --> 01:25:30,799
I said they were entrusted to
me, Esma’s and Selim’s legacy.

988
01:25:30,800 --> 01:25:32,280
I took care of them like roses.

989
01:25:36,120 --> 01:25:39,320
Why are you shouting again?
Your voices reached upstairs.

990
01:25:40,560 --> 01:25:43,360
Good you came. Answer me.

991
01:25:44,360 --> 01:25:45,520
What is going on, Mercan?

992
01:25:47,080 --> 01:25:48,240
Tahir and Eylül.

993
01:25:57,200 --> 01:26:01,320
Did you really lock those two
small children in that cold basement?

994
01:26:01,720 --> 01:26:03,920
Were you truly capable of such cruelty?

995
01:26:04,960 --> 01:26:09,400
We did nothing cruel. You were
small, you would not remember.

996
01:26:10,360 --> 01:26:13,639
They were very unruly, aggressive.
We could not handle them.

997
01:26:13,640 --> 01:26:17,479
Time passed, I do not remember clearly but

998
01:26:17,480 --> 01:26:21,560
maybe we locked them in the basement
once or twice to calm them down.

999
01:26:22,960 --> 01:26:28,040
But it is not true we neglected them.
We provided everything they needed.

1000
01:26:29,040 --> 01:26:32,279
When I asked you before,
you did not even remember.

1001
01:26:32,280 --> 01:26:34,560
You said you did not know Eylül.

1002
01:26:35,360 --> 01:26:36,959
I do not know what to do anymore.

1003
01:26:36,960 --> 01:26:39,680
I do not know who to believe, who to trust.

1004
01:26:39,880 --> 01:26:42,719
I do not know who is telling
the truth, who is lying.

1005
01:26:42,720 --> 01:26:49,920
It feels like I am in limbo
and I do not know which way to go.

1006
01:26:51,480 --> 01:26:53,799
My daughter, your mother and I…

1007
01:26:53,800 --> 01:26:56,720
Do not touch me. Do not.

1008
01:27:08,360 --> 01:27:11,080
The day I learned his sibling
died, I should have killed him too.

1009
01:27:22,200 --> 01:27:26,120
So what now? Should Haydar try to run?

1010
01:27:27,760 --> 01:27:29,480
I have not forgotten my goal. Do not worry.

1011
01:27:30,040 --> 01:27:31,640
I warned the men. They are all on alert.

1012
01:27:32,840 --> 01:27:36,520
Haydar cannot escape anywhere.
The plan has not changed.

1013
01:27:38,360 --> 01:27:41,120
If you find the time between
consoling Ms. Mercan, of course.

1014
01:27:42,440 --> 01:27:43,959
Now it is time to stand together.

1015
01:27:43,960 --> 01:27:46,040
Hard days passed, harder
ones await us, friends.

1016
01:27:47,560 --> 01:27:49,920
I have no patience left.

1017
01:27:50,280 --> 01:27:55,280
I do not want to see that man
walking around the mansion freely.

1018
01:27:57,120 --> 01:27:59,520
Do whatever is necessary, immediately.

1019
01:28:11,320 --> 01:28:15,360
What do you think, Ateş? Are
we finishing Haydar right away?

1020
01:28:20,120 --> 01:28:24,159
I know you are torn. Not
because you pity Haydar,

1021
01:28:24,160 --> 01:28:27,360
but because you do not want
Mercan to suffer. I know that too.

1022
01:28:28,320 --> 01:28:30,360
I would not want to be in your place.

1023
01:28:35,280 --> 01:28:36,960
Our plan regarding Haydar has not changed.

1024
01:28:41,320 --> 01:28:42,400
Even despite Mercan?

1025
01:28:44,080 --> 01:28:49,400
Despite Mercan. This is separate from that.

1026
01:29:08,720 --> 01:29:13,360
Hard days await us. My God, help us.

1027
01:29:29,280 --> 01:29:30,400
Mom.

1028
01:29:32,000 --> 01:29:33,280
Yes, my child.

1029
01:29:35,040 --> 01:29:36,160
Thank you.

1030
01:29:37,440 --> 01:29:38,440
Enjoy your meal.

1031
01:29:48,760 --> 01:29:50,720
I am deeply hurt by you, my son.

1032
01:29:53,840 --> 01:29:56,479
From the day you were born, I
cared for you like my own eyes…

1033
01:29:56,480 --> 01:30:00,200
fed you, raised you,
brought you to this age.

1034
01:30:03,840 --> 01:30:05,440
But what did you do?

1035
01:30:06,680 --> 01:30:09,800
You left without a word
and married that girl.

1036
01:30:14,320 --> 01:30:17,680
You disregarded all my years of effort.

1037
01:30:18,240 --> 01:30:19,240
You trampled me.

1038
01:30:22,680 --> 01:30:24,440
Do not say that, mom.

1039
01:30:26,640 --> 01:30:27,840
You are precious to me.

1040
01:30:31,920 --> 01:30:33,880
You are my life, my very breath.

1041
01:30:36,880 --> 01:30:39,920
Would anyone harm the one they love most?

1042
01:30:41,720 --> 01:30:43,560
You erased me, my son.

1043
01:30:48,080 --> 01:30:56,080
Mom, my intention was not to hurt you.

1044
01:31:02,480 --> 01:31:04,320
I love Zehra deeply.

1045
01:31:05,720 --> 01:31:08,840
I wanted to build a home with her.

1046
01:31:13,280 --> 01:31:17,440
Because I knew you would not
approve, I chose this path.

1047
01:31:21,800 --> 01:31:23,840
How do you know I would not approve?

1048
01:31:24,600 --> 01:31:25,600
Did you ask me?

1049
01:31:29,080 --> 01:31:31,120
Let us say I assumed.

1050
01:31:33,760 --> 01:31:36,159
That is not how things work, Mr. Berat.

1051
01:31:36,160 --> 01:31:37,880
There is propriety, there is order.

1052
01:31:39,680 --> 01:31:45,640
What good is a home built after
crushing and ignoring your family?

1053
01:31:47,840 --> 01:31:49,800
Forgive me, mom.

1054
01:31:50,840 --> 01:31:51,920
We did something reckless.

1055
01:31:58,080 --> 01:32:00,240
Give me one chance like
the one you gave Çiçek.

1056
01:32:01,200 --> 01:32:05,039
You accepted Malik as a son in law…

1057
01:32:05,040 --> 01:32:07,920
accept Zehra as your daughter in law too.

1058
01:32:10,360 --> 01:32:12,200
Do you really love this girl that much?

1059
01:32:15,000 --> 01:32:16,160
More than you know, mom.

1060
01:32:51,440 --> 01:32:54,399
All that happened…

1061
01:32:54,400 --> 01:32:58,000
so much pain, cruelty, torture…

1062
01:33:00,240 --> 01:33:02,280
it is so heavy.

1063
01:33:05,760 --> 01:33:07,680
A child died.

1064
01:33:08,680 --> 01:33:11,160
A child died.

1065
01:33:18,480 --> 01:33:20,120
My God, what kind of trial is this?

1066
01:33:22,320 --> 01:33:24,360
Please give me strength to endure.

1067
01:33:25,680 --> 01:33:28,280
Please give me strength.

1068
01:33:56,680 --> 01:33:58,280
My father…

1069
01:33:58,480 --> 01:34:01,680
Did my father really lock
Tahir and Eylül in here?

1070
01:34:05,200 --> 01:34:07,280
It is so hard to believe.

1071
01:34:10,080 --> 01:34:13,039
A person with a heart…

1072
01:34:13,040 --> 01:34:15,960
how does he do this to
two defenseless children?

1073
01:34:17,240 --> 01:34:18,480
How?

1074
01:34:20,880 --> 01:34:21,880
How?

1075
01:34:24,200 --> 01:34:26,120
How?

1076
01:34:49,600 --> 01:34:51,160
Mercan.

1077
01:34:58,680 --> 01:35:00,560
I was worried about you. Are you okay?

1078
01:35:08,600 --> 01:35:10,120
How could I be okay?

1079
01:35:12,680 --> 01:35:13,680
You are right.

1080
01:35:17,160 --> 01:35:20,039
In a situation like this…

1081
01:35:20,040 --> 01:35:22,120
I do not know what I can
do to make you feel better.

1082
01:35:23,760 --> 01:35:26,240
You want me to feel better?

1083
01:35:28,920 --> 01:35:30,720
Then show me a way out.

1084
01:35:32,400 --> 01:35:34,920
I do not want to stay in limbo anymore.

1085
01:35:38,760 --> 01:35:41,040
I can only show you the real way out.

1086
01:35:42,920 --> 01:35:44,200
And you already know the truth.

1087
01:35:47,200 --> 01:35:51,400
Your father took my mother, my father,
my sibling, my whole family from me.

1088
01:35:51,840 --> 01:35:52,840
This is the truth.

1089
01:35:53,800 --> 01:35:56,040
I swore revenge at their graves.

1090
01:35:56,920 --> 01:35:57,920
This is the truth.

1091
01:35:59,160 --> 01:36:01,560
I promised myself I would
not turn back from my revenge.

1092
01:36:02,480 --> 01:36:03,480
This is the truth.

1093
01:36:07,800 --> 01:36:11,760
I only want justice for
the lives I lost, Mercan.

1094
01:36:13,360 --> 01:36:14,360
This is the truth.

1095
01:36:16,640 --> 01:36:17,960
So you want justice.

1096
01:36:20,000 --> 01:36:21,440
Then what was my sin?

1097
01:36:23,600 --> 01:36:25,560
Why did you put me through this?

1098
01:36:28,720 --> 01:36:30,880
I was just a small
child like you once were.

1099
01:36:32,160 --> 01:36:35,480
Did I hurt you? Did I burn your heart?

1100
01:36:37,840 --> 01:36:38,840
No.

1101
01:36:40,920 --> 01:36:43,000
You are the most innocent
person in this story.

1102
01:36:45,680 --> 01:36:49,240
I am the most innocent one,
huh? What did that change?

1103
01:36:50,200 --> 01:36:51,200
Me.

1104
01:36:54,840 --> 01:36:59,760
This love was something I did not
calculate while planning revenge.

1105
01:37:04,880 --> 01:37:07,400
At first, I could not
even admit it to myself.

1106
01:37:08,280 --> 01:37:12,280
Because the idea of falling in love
with my enemy’s daughter drove me mad.

1107
01:37:43,600 --> 01:37:46,160
There was a fierce battle
between my heart and my mind.

1108
01:37:48,560 --> 01:37:50,200
I was in limbo too.

1109
01:37:56,040 --> 01:37:58,520
I fell into such a love…

1110
01:38:00,800 --> 01:38:02,720
that my heart emerged victorious.

1111
01:38:11,520 --> 01:38:13,440
And now I am paying the price.

1112
01:39:08,840 --> 01:39:11,120
Come here, Aslı. We need
to talk. I said come here.

1113
01:39:11,640 --> 01:39:13,840
What are you doing? What is your problem?

1114
01:39:14,680 --> 01:39:16,440
Are you that curious about my problem?

1115
01:39:18,000 --> 01:39:19,200
This is my problem.

1116
01:39:22,480 --> 01:39:24,880
Say something. Convince
me. I am begging you.

1117
01:39:25,440 --> 01:39:28,560
Let me believe this is a lie
so I can burn it and believe you.

1118
01:39:30,360 --> 01:39:31,520
Where did you find this?

1119
01:39:36,800 --> 01:39:39,280
Is this really the question
you are asking me right now, Aslı?

1120
01:39:40,200 --> 01:39:42,240
Let us say I found it somewhere.

1121
01:39:43,720 --> 01:39:46,120
Let me tell you the real
question you should ask.

1122
01:39:49,120 --> 01:39:50,560
Why did you do this to us, Aslı?

1123
01:39:52,440 --> 01:39:55,080
I did what I believed was right.

1124
01:39:57,720 --> 01:40:00,679
Betraying us is what
you believed was right?

1125
01:40:00,680 --> 01:40:04,160
What betrayal? Who did I betray?

1126
01:40:05,920 --> 01:40:07,839
Mercan and Ateş were getting close.

1127
01:40:07,840 --> 01:40:11,000
The only person who could
separate them was Nezir.

1128
01:40:11,320 --> 01:40:13,880
I found a loophole in
the contract and used it.

1129
01:40:15,680 --> 01:40:18,480
I wanted him to tear Mercan and Ateş apart.

1130
01:40:19,320 --> 01:40:20,920
But Nezir did not use his chance well.

1131
01:40:22,160 --> 01:40:25,120
Whatever the case, it does not
change the fact you betrayed us.

1132
01:40:26,320 --> 01:40:29,720
You are wrong. I stayed loyal to the plan.

1133
01:40:30,680 --> 01:40:32,599
The real betrayal was Ateş.

1134
01:40:32,600 --> 01:40:35,000
He fell in love with his enemy’s daughter.

1135
01:40:36,840 --> 01:40:42,160
But I told you. I warned you
many times. You did not listen.

1136
01:40:43,720 --> 01:40:46,040
So I took initiative and took precautions.

1137
01:40:47,200 --> 01:40:50,320
Looking at where we are now, was I wrong?

1138
01:40:54,800 --> 01:40:57,360
Nothing you say excuses your betrayal.

1139
01:40:58,600 --> 01:41:01,320
You knowingly chose the dark side.

1140
01:41:03,720 --> 01:41:08,120
You are no different from the
people we came here to take revenge on.

1141
01:41:09,440 --> 01:41:12,960
How could you do this? I
do not recognize you anymore.

1142
01:41:20,000 --> 01:41:22,240
You will not tell Ateş, right?

1143
01:41:25,440 --> 01:41:28,200
Cemal, please do not tell him.

1144
01:41:29,600 --> 01:41:32,080
If you care about me even
a little, do not tell him.

1145
01:41:41,320 --> 01:41:44,240
I will lose him forever.

1146
01:41:45,440 --> 01:41:48,640
He will never even
look at me again. Please.

1147
01:41:53,640 --> 01:41:58,800
If you know me even a little, you
know I will not hide anything from Ateş.

1148
01:42:00,920 --> 01:42:03,479
Unfortunately, he has
no time for you right now.

1149
01:42:03,480 --> 01:42:05,840
But do not get comfortable.

1150
01:42:07,480 --> 01:42:10,160
One day the truth will come out.

1151
01:42:11,120 --> 01:42:14,279
And when it does, deal with your own mess.

1152
01:42:14,280 --> 01:42:15,840
Get rid of Nezir as soon as possible.

1153
01:43:22,280 --> 01:43:24,280
I am very sorry.

1154
01:43:28,320 --> 01:43:30,320
Me too.

1155
01:47:17,120 --> 01:47:19,039
Were you eavesdropping?

1156
01:47:19,040 --> 01:47:22,360
No point. I was alone in the room.

1157
01:47:23,080 --> 01:47:24,720
What would I listen at your door for?

1158
01:47:26,120 --> 01:47:27,280
Something you did not do?

1159
01:47:29,440 --> 01:47:32,680
Oh dear, did you become a victim of love?

1160
01:47:38,000 --> 01:47:39,000
Get out of my way.

1161
01:47:40,440 --> 01:47:43,400
All right, wait. Let us talk for a second.

1162
01:47:44,720 --> 01:47:48,800
You do not want to? Fine, I will talk.

1163
01:47:50,600 --> 01:47:53,439
Remember I told you the
other day you were naive?

1164
01:47:53,440 --> 01:47:55,800
I am raising the stakes.

1165
01:47:56,840 --> 01:47:59,680
You are the most foolish
person I have ever met.

1166
01:48:01,440 --> 01:48:05,520
You believed Ateş’s
love, despite my warnings.

1167
01:48:06,800 --> 01:48:09,400
Well, better late than never.

1168
01:48:11,240 --> 01:48:15,560
Enough. Enough. Leave me alone, all of you.

1169
01:48:22,320 --> 01:48:30,320
We will fall. But we are not done
with you and your family yet. Not yet.

1170
01:48:57,000 --> 01:48:59,880
I thought something warm would help.

1171
01:49:00,600 --> 01:49:01,600
Thanks.

1172
01:49:01,720 --> 01:49:02,720
Enjoy.

1173
01:49:54,880 --> 01:49:57,920
I think I am hurting everyone lately.

1174
01:49:59,120 --> 01:50:03,240
There is nothing I can do for
the glass. But there is for Mercan.

1175
01:50:05,240 --> 01:50:06,600
I think you should go talk to her.

1176
01:50:10,440 --> 01:50:18,360
I did. It did not help. She is deeply hurt.

1177
01:50:26,080 --> 01:50:28,400
She thinks I used her for revenge.

1178
01:50:29,840 --> 01:50:31,480
She does not believe I love her.

1179
01:50:32,760 --> 01:50:33,999
She does not believe it, huh?

1180
01:50:34,000 --> 01:50:39,040
Then what, does she believe her father?

1181
01:50:42,800 --> 01:50:45,759
She does not know who to believe.

1182
01:50:45,760 --> 01:50:48,280
And she is not wrong.

1183
01:50:51,640 --> 01:50:55,640
Her father and I both lied to her.

1184
01:50:58,720 --> 01:51:00,239
Not being able to help her,

1185
01:51:00,240 --> 01:51:03,399
having her so close yet so far from me,

1186
01:51:03,400 --> 01:51:06,720
hurts me deeply.

1187
01:51:13,200 --> 01:51:17,160
So love and revenge cannot coexist.

1188
01:51:22,840 --> 01:51:30,840
They must. I will not give
up my love or my revenge.

1189
01:51:53,000 --> 01:51:54,719
I am still so confused.

1190
01:51:54,720 --> 01:51:59,479
So the man we thought was
Ateş was actually Tahir.

1191
01:51:59,480 --> 01:52:04,520
And he says such unthinkable
things about your family.

1192
01:52:05,120 --> 01:52:07,600
Why would Uncle Haydar do such a thing?

1193
01:52:09,880 --> 01:52:12,000
They deny everything.

1194
01:52:14,040 --> 01:52:18,680
I do not know. One cannot
imagine such things about family.

1195
01:52:19,760 --> 01:52:24,720
Ateş’s words echo in my
ears, my father’s answers too.

1196
01:52:27,840 --> 01:52:29,800
What am I in the middle of?

1197
01:52:33,960 --> 01:52:35,520
I am very sorry, Mercan.

1198
01:52:36,200 --> 01:52:36,600
Why?

1199
01:52:37,160 --> 01:52:42,640
I encouraged you about
Ateş too. I regret it deeply.

1200
01:52:43,120 --> 01:52:45,800
Had I known, I would never
have supported this relationship.

1201
01:52:46,440 --> 01:52:48,520
How could you have known?

1202
01:52:49,560 --> 01:52:54,080
Look, even I failed to see
what was right in front of me.

1203
01:53:01,040 --> 01:53:06,080
Ateş, fool. You destroyed yourself.

1204
01:53:06,400 --> 01:53:09,440
Well done. Thanks to
you, Mercan will be mine.

1205
01:53:14,640 --> 01:53:15,920
Greetings, Mercan.

1206
01:53:17,600 --> 01:53:19,080
Your father just told me everything.

1207
01:53:20,600 --> 01:53:21,760
Honestly, I am not surprised.

1208
01:53:22,600 --> 01:53:26,080
I told you many times from the
start that man was dangerous.

1209
01:53:32,480 --> 01:53:33,800
Brother, what are you doing?

1210
01:53:35,440 --> 01:53:40,160
Just say the word. I will
make them all pay right now.

1211
01:53:40,680 --> 01:53:43,680
What are you saying, Nezir?
What do you think you are doing?

1212
01:53:44,880 --> 01:53:47,200
I will not allow you to
harm him, no matter what.

1213
01:53:49,800 --> 01:53:51,719
Put that gun down right
now. Do you understand?

1214
01:53:51,720 --> 01:53:53,760
Or you will answer to me.

1215
01:53:55,720 --> 01:53:57,840
Mercan, you do not understand me.

1216
01:53:58,440 --> 01:54:02,399
I would do anything for you.
To protect you. Because I…

1217
01:54:02,400 --> 01:54:03,400
Please.

1218
01:54:07,280 --> 01:54:09,320
I am dropping the subject
out of respect for Demet.

1219
01:54:09,880 --> 01:54:12,560
Let us not drag this out. I do
not want you involved. Understood?

1220
01:54:15,600 --> 01:54:20,440
Everything done to you concerns me too.

1221
01:54:22,080 --> 01:54:26,560
But know this. I am always by your side.

1222
01:54:28,880 --> 01:54:32,000
If you will excuse me, I will rest.

1223
01:54:32,600 --> 01:54:34,840
Mercan. Do not be sad.

1224
01:54:35,880 --> 01:54:37,719
These days will pass.

1225
01:54:37,720 --> 01:54:39,880
Insallah, Demet.

1226
01:54:40,720 --> 01:54:44,000
As I said, Mercan. You
only need to call me.

1227
01:55:18,680 --> 01:55:19,520
Will you excuse me?

1228
01:55:19,521 --> 01:55:23,960
No. I will not let you pass until we talk.

1229
01:55:25,160 --> 01:55:26,560
I do not want to talk.

1230
01:55:30,360 --> 01:55:35,920
Do not punish me with
silence. Not me, not yourself.

1231
01:55:39,280 --> 01:55:44,720
I do not know what to
say. Or what to believe.

1232
01:55:45,520 --> 01:55:51,040
And you are responsible for this.
I am like this because of your lies.

1233
01:55:53,680 --> 01:55:57,520
I realized I valued you
far more than you deserved.

1234
01:56:02,680 --> 01:56:09,560
I loved you far more than you
deserved. I regret it deeply.

1235
01:56:11,960 --> 01:56:15,040
Can I go now? I am
exhausted. I want to rest.

1236
01:56:17,240 --> 01:56:18,240
So you are tired?

1237
01:56:21,000 --> 01:56:24,239
What are you doing?
Put me down. Put me down.

1238
01:56:24,240 --> 01:56:25,616
I will not let go. Stop struggling.

1239
01:56:25,640 --> 01:56:27,120
I said put me down.

1240
01:56:32,440 --> 01:56:34,199
Put me down. Let go.

1241
01:56:34,200 --> 01:56:36,320
Enough already. Put me down.

1242
01:56:37,840 --> 01:56:41,160
Someone will see us. Enough. Put me down.

1243
01:56:50,520 --> 01:56:51,520
Get in here. Sit.

1244
01:56:51,800 --> 01:56:53,920
Let go. I am not going anywhere with you.

1245
01:56:54,200 --> 01:56:55,480
You are coming. Behave yourself.

1246
01:56:56,800 --> 01:56:59,360
Bully. What do you think you are doing?

1247
01:57:01,600 --> 01:57:03,400
You cannot take me
anywhere by force. Let go.

1248
01:57:03,600 --> 01:57:08,640
I can stay like this for hours. No
problem at all. I would even be happy.

1249
01:57:11,280 --> 01:57:15,080
Either you stop resisting and
come with me, or the choice is yours.

1250
01:57:41,040 --> 01:57:43,280
Why are you looking like that?

1251
01:57:46,360 --> 01:57:47,680
I still see myself.

1252
01:57:52,000 --> 01:57:56,240
I did not say I did not love
you. I said I regret loving you.

1253
01:58:04,000 --> 01:58:08,600
Do not resist. You have nowhere to run.

1254
01:58:24,840 --> 01:58:26,320
At least tell me where we are going.

1255
01:58:27,240 --> 01:58:28,600
You will see when we get there.

1256
01:58:30,800 --> 01:58:34,400
You will see, huh. Annoying.

1257
01:58:42,440 --> 01:58:49,760
Zehra is right. Look, we are
working on our second day of marriage.

1258
01:58:52,240 --> 01:58:53,880
Honeymoon talk is nonsense.

1259
01:58:56,600 --> 01:58:57,600
Damn.

1260
01:59:01,200 --> 01:59:02,680
Anyway.

1261
01:59:10,320 --> 01:59:11,560
Bismillah.

1262
01:59:14,920 --> 01:59:15,920
Berat.

1263
01:59:26,320 --> 01:59:28,400
I know you are still angry at me.

1264
01:59:29,560 --> 01:59:31,680
I came knowing you might snap at me.

1265
01:59:33,280 --> 01:59:35,719
Do not worry, I will not bother you long.

1266
01:59:35,720 --> 01:59:38,200
I will say a few things and go.

1267
01:59:39,960 --> 01:59:40,960
Congratulations.

1268
01:59:42,760 --> 01:59:46,040
I hope your marriage with
Zehra lasts a lifetime.

1269
01:59:47,920 --> 01:59:49,080
Is that what you came to say?

1270
01:59:50,360 --> 01:59:52,560
Of course. What did you think?

1271
01:59:55,560 --> 01:59:57,840
Nothing. I thought nothing.

1272
02:00:00,520 --> 02:00:01,880
You know what, Malik?

1273
02:00:04,640 --> 02:00:06,880
You are the first to congratulate me.

1274
02:00:09,400 --> 02:00:10,400
Thanks.

1275
02:00:11,160 --> 02:00:12,160
Thanks.

1276
02:00:13,840 --> 02:00:15,920
Do you know what I realized just now?

1277
02:00:17,560 --> 02:00:21,560
Old friends do not become
enemies that easily. Thanks.

1278
02:00:22,600 --> 02:00:23,600
Thanks.

1279
02:00:25,360 --> 02:00:27,120
Malik, Arabic 02.

1280
02:00:28,120 --> 02:00:29,120
So?

1281
02:00:29,200 --> 02:00:30,840
I am really glad you think like this.

1282
02:00:39,480 --> 02:00:41,200
I missed being like this.

1283
02:00:41,480 --> 02:00:42,560
Me too, you know.

1284
02:00:42,760 --> 02:00:44,279
Just like the old days.

1285
02:00:44,280 --> 02:00:47,640
Come on then. Grab hold
of this. Let us do it.

1286
02:00:48,000 --> 02:00:49,320
You immediately put me to work.

1287
02:00:50,200 --> 02:00:53,360
Come on. Be careful. Do not hurt yourself.

1288
02:00:53,480 --> 02:00:54,960
Then Çiçek will come nagging.

1289
02:00:55,560 --> 02:00:56,880
It will not happen, do not worry.

1290
02:00:57,240 --> 02:00:58,240
Careful.

1291
02:00:59,320 --> 02:01:01,560
Look, how would you lift this without me?

1292
02:01:01,640 --> 02:01:02,640
Hold it.

1293
02:01:04,200 --> 02:01:05,200
That is it.

1294
02:01:08,800 --> 02:01:09,800
Malik.

1295
02:01:11,520 --> 02:01:12,520
Thanks, brother.

1296
02:01:14,520 --> 02:01:15,520
Thanks.

1297
02:01:31,880 --> 02:01:33,680
If you want, I can
treat you to a meal today.

1298
02:01:33,960 --> 02:01:35,200
Great. I know a good place.

1299
02:01:37,080 --> 02:01:38,720
What was that earlier, brother?

1300
02:01:39,880 --> 02:01:40,880
What did I do?

1301
02:01:41,720 --> 02:01:44,640
Putting a gun on the
table, threats and all.

1302
02:01:47,160 --> 02:01:48,280
Are you a bandit?

1303
02:01:48,920 --> 02:01:50,440
What else was I supposed to do, Demet?

1304
02:01:51,040 --> 02:01:52,440
Did you not see Mercan’s state?

1305
02:01:53,280 --> 02:01:54,960
The poor girl is shattered.

1306
02:01:57,120 --> 02:02:00,000
I am madly in love with Mercan.

1307
02:02:02,920 --> 02:02:03,440
Do you not understand?

1308
02:02:03,880 --> 02:02:05,360
You protect the one you love.

1309
02:02:06,400 --> 02:02:07,400
I would die for her.

1310
02:02:07,720 --> 02:02:08,880
If needed, I would kill.

1311
02:02:09,280 --> 02:02:10,720
Say whatever you want.

1312
02:02:11,280 --> 02:02:14,320
I will never understand this mindset.

1313
02:02:15,160 --> 02:02:16,160
Fine.

1314
02:02:16,240 --> 02:02:17,560
Then do not tire yourself.

1315
02:02:18,400 --> 02:02:19,960
Do you want my happiness?

1316
02:02:20,840 --> 02:02:23,239
What kind of question is that?
Of course I want your happiness.

1317
02:02:23,240 --> 02:02:27,400
Then instead of posturing,
help me fix things with Mercan.

1318
02:02:30,880 --> 02:02:33,080
Brother, I think you
should see a psychologist.

1319
02:02:34,000 --> 02:02:37,280
I am honestly worried
about your mental health.

1320
02:02:38,960 --> 02:02:41,040
Let us go. I am not eating anything.

1321
02:02:44,640 --> 02:02:46,720
I do not care what anyone says.

1322
02:02:49,080 --> 02:02:50,600
In the end, Mercan will be mine.

1323
02:03:01,200 --> 02:03:03,320
Zehra, pass me that strainer.

1324
02:03:05,400 --> 02:03:07,080
Would it hurt you to get it yourself?

1325
02:03:07,560 --> 02:03:08,920
I do not feel like myself today.

1326
02:03:09,120 --> 02:03:10,960
I cannot even move my finger.

1327
02:03:20,920 --> 02:03:21,920
Good luck.

1328
02:03:22,480 --> 02:03:23,560
Welcome home, my husband.

1329
02:03:25,520 --> 02:03:26,520
Thanks.

1330
02:03:27,360 --> 02:03:28,440
You must be tired.

1331
02:03:29,080 --> 02:03:31,520
Come sit. I will pour you some tea.

1332
02:03:32,120 --> 02:03:33,120
That would be good.

1333
02:03:37,800 --> 02:03:40,840
Look how she jumped up
when she saw my brother.

1334
02:03:41,760 --> 02:03:45,240
For God’s sake, I have never
seen someone act this well.

1335
02:03:47,520 --> 02:03:49,800
It is not the girl’s fault. It is Berat’s.

1336
02:03:51,800 --> 02:03:54,040
Look, he is practically
falling into her mouth.

1337
02:03:56,200 --> 02:03:57,200
My God.

1338
02:04:00,000 --> 02:04:01,440
Here you go, my husband.

1339
02:04:01,960 --> 02:04:03,400
Thank you, my wife.

1340
02:04:03,680 --> 02:04:05,640
May it be sweet as honey for you.

1341
02:04:07,320 --> 02:04:09,720
Oh my God.

1342
02:04:14,200 --> 02:04:16,000
The tea is so good.
You can tell you made it.

1343
02:04:17,600 --> 02:04:20,400
Brother, open this for me, please.

1344
02:04:23,680 --> 02:04:25,040
What do you mean?

1345
02:04:29,440 --> 02:04:30,560
Why should Berat open it?

1346
02:04:31,400 --> 02:04:32,760
My husband is tired.

1347
02:04:33,720 --> 02:04:35,080
If you cannot, call Malik.

1348
02:04:39,000 --> 02:04:41,240
I am very tired, you know.

1349
02:04:41,520 --> 02:04:42,879
Work has drained my faith.

1350
02:04:42,880 --> 02:04:44,640
I mean it that much.

1351
02:04:49,440 --> 02:04:50,440
Oh my.

1352
02:04:51,400 --> 02:04:52,416
Did we tell you to dig trenches?

1353
02:04:52,440 --> 02:04:53,880
We just asked you to open the lid.

1354
02:04:53,920 --> 02:04:55,680
What is this? What
kind of behavior is this?

1355
02:04:56,240 --> 02:04:57,240
No.

1356
02:04:57,520 --> 02:04:58,800
My husband will lose strength.

1357
02:04:59,080 --> 02:05:00,800
My God, give me patience.

1358
02:05:07,800 --> 02:05:08,800
Drink.

1359
02:05:09,040 --> 02:05:10,040
Enjoy.

1360
02:05:10,320 --> 02:05:11,320
Thank you.

1361
02:05:13,320 --> 02:05:15,000
Give it here, my daughter. I will open it.

1362
02:05:24,600 --> 02:05:26,280
Here.

1363
02:05:30,840 --> 02:05:32,880
Why did you bring me here?

1364
02:05:34,840 --> 02:05:36,920
I know you like this place.

1365
02:05:37,840 --> 02:05:39,400
You used to come here often with Demet.

1366
02:05:41,240 --> 02:05:42,600
You know everything.

1367
02:05:43,720 --> 02:05:45,520
Who knows how long you
have been watching me.

1368
02:05:47,880 --> 02:05:49,560
I tried not to watch too much.

1369
02:05:51,080 --> 02:05:52,320
Because you enchanted me.

1370
02:05:56,200 --> 02:05:58,240
And that could have pulled
me away from my purpose.

1371
02:06:01,920 --> 02:06:03,400
Should I be happy now?

1372
02:06:08,160 --> 02:06:09,800
I think you should not bother yourself.

1373
02:06:11,000 --> 02:06:12,480
Do not waste your words either.

1374
02:06:12,920 --> 02:06:14,360
I do not feel like believing you.

1375
02:06:15,720 --> 02:06:17,280
You were writing your name in the sand.

1376
02:06:22,280 --> 02:06:23,520
Only Mercan.

1377
02:06:26,200 --> 02:06:30,080
I was so afraid you would
write another name next to it.

1378
02:06:34,800 --> 02:06:35,800
You never did.

1379
02:06:40,640 --> 02:06:45,880
One day after you left, I
wrote Ateş next to your name.

1380
02:06:50,120 --> 02:06:51,960
I watched it for a moment.

1381
02:06:53,760 --> 02:06:55,680
Then I got angry with myself and erased it.

1382
02:06:58,160 --> 02:07:03,040
I knew then you would be my
downfall, yet I thought I could stop it.

1383
02:07:06,360 --> 02:07:09,960
I could not. After that,
I tried to stay away.

1384
02:07:12,600 --> 02:07:13,680
But my battle never ended.

1385
02:07:15,240 --> 02:07:16,800
Because of you.

1386
02:07:21,320 --> 02:07:22,640
Am I supposed to be moved?

1387
02:07:24,080 --> 02:07:26,120
Not to move you. Just so you know.

1388
02:07:27,120 --> 02:07:28,120
These are the facts.

1389
02:07:30,760 --> 02:07:31,960
Do you know what the truth is?

1390
02:07:33,480 --> 02:07:37,360
You wrote the name Ateş next to Mercan.

1391
02:07:40,000 --> 02:07:42,479
If you had chosen to write Tahir,

1392
02:07:42,480 --> 02:07:44,800
maybe our lives would
be very different now.

1393
02:07:47,400 --> 02:07:50,440
But you chose Ateş.

1394
02:07:54,440 --> 02:07:56,240
And you fell in love with Ateş.

1395
02:07:57,760 --> 02:07:58,760
Yes.

1396
02:07:58,960 --> 02:08:00,880
I fell in love with Ateş.

1397
02:08:02,240 --> 02:08:03,960
Deeply.

1398
02:08:08,200 --> 02:08:11,400
That is why you are the greatest
disappointment of my life, Ateş.

1399
02:08:26,760 --> 02:08:28,960
You erased your name from the sand, right?

1400
02:08:29,840 --> 02:08:32,720
I will erase you from my heart.

1401
02:08:33,240 --> 02:08:35,400
There will not even be a trace left.

1402
02:08:38,280 --> 02:08:41,960
As if I never loved you.

1403
02:09:07,400 --> 02:09:08,400
It is over.

1404
02:09:11,480 --> 02:09:13,600
All that remains of me is wreckage.

1405
02:09:14,800 --> 02:09:16,320
Is it really that easy to tear out?

1406
02:09:18,320 --> 02:09:23,760
If it were that easy, I would not
be standing before you in this pain.

1407
02:09:26,920 --> 02:09:30,480
It will be very hard. I
know. But I will succeed.

1408
02:09:50,360 --> 02:09:51,800
I will not lose to you again.

1409
02:09:54,040 --> 02:09:55,560
Do not deceive yourself.

1410
02:09:56,840 --> 02:09:58,720
There are invisible bonds between us.

1411
02:10:00,040 --> 02:10:02,120
Like a mark written by fate.

1412
02:10:04,080 --> 02:10:05,080
We cannot break free.

1413
02:10:07,480 --> 02:10:08,720
I know it from myself.

1414
02:10:11,160 --> 02:10:12,160
You know it too.

1415
02:10:51,520 --> 02:10:52,520
Here, take it.

1416
02:10:55,520 --> 02:10:56,520
Go on, eat.

1417
02:10:57,600 --> 02:11:00,880
One of the best charities is
feeding what is given to you.

1418
02:11:05,800 --> 02:11:07,720
Are you feeding the cat?

1419
02:11:07,880 --> 02:11:09,120
Çiçek, come here. Yes.

1420
02:11:09,800 --> 02:11:11,800
She emptied all the food bowls.

1421
02:11:12,240 --> 02:11:13,840
The kitten ate everything.

1422
02:11:13,960 --> 02:11:15,680
I brought you tea.

1423
02:11:15,960 --> 02:11:16,760
It will warm you up.

1424
02:11:16,960 --> 02:11:18,000
Bless your hands, Çiçek.

1425
02:11:18,280 --> 02:11:19,440
Tea will be great.

1426
02:11:19,880 --> 02:11:21,520
Then let us trade.

1427
02:11:21,760 --> 02:11:23,640
I will take the tea, you take the kitten.

1428
02:11:24,200 --> 02:11:24,960
Come here.

1429
02:11:25,040 --> 02:11:26,536
See, she loves me. She will not let go.

1430
02:11:26,560 --> 02:11:27,560
You see.

1431
02:11:27,600 --> 02:11:28,680
She loves me too.

1432
02:11:33,680 --> 02:11:35,200
Do you want to feed her as well?

1433
02:11:40,520 --> 02:11:42,920
Çiçek, I am so happy.

1434
02:11:42,960 --> 02:11:45,560
We are just like the old days right now.

1435
02:11:46,200 --> 02:11:48,120
Yes, I am very happy too.

1436
02:11:48,360 --> 02:11:51,000
I find myself smiling like
crazy when I think about it.

1437
02:11:53,040 --> 02:11:56,360
Çiçek, we have been
together almost two years now.

1438
02:11:56,920 --> 02:11:59,360
But look, Berat went before us
and married the girl he loves.

1439
02:12:00,360 --> 02:12:02,160
I swear I am jealous of my brother in law.

1440
02:12:02,600 --> 02:12:03,879
He entered married life before us.

1441
02:12:03,880 --> 02:12:07,320
Really, who would have thought?

1442
02:12:08,040 --> 02:12:10,040
And with Zehra too.

1443
02:12:10,560 --> 02:12:11,880
Right?

1444
02:12:12,400 --> 02:12:13,760
What do you think?

1445
02:12:15,200 --> 02:12:17,280
My patience is gone.

1446
02:12:18,280 --> 02:12:19,480
I cannot endure it anymore.

1447
02:12:20,400 --> 02:12:23,240
Let us start the wedding
procedures as soon as possible.

1448
02:12:24,280 --> 02:12:27,080
I want it too. I cannot endure it either.

1449
02:12:30,000 --> 02:12:32,999
But we need to convince your family.

1450
02:12:33,000 --> 02:12:36,080
So everyone is content and no one is hurt.

1451
02:12:36,360 --> 02:12:38,960
That will happen, Çiçek. It will.

1452
02:12:40,720 --> 02:12:41,720
Right?

1453
02:12:43,320 --> 02:12:46,000
Oh my little one.

1454
02:12:48,040 --> 02:12:49,920
Is she not adorable?

1455
02:12:50,240 --> 02:12:51,320
She is.

1456
02:13:16,120 --> 02:13:17,120
Demet.

1457
02:13:18,680 --> 02:13:20,400
Shall we talk for a bit?

1458
02:13:20,880 --> 02:13:21,880
Of course.

1459
02:13:24,560 --> 02:13:26,400
Yes, I am listening.

1460
02:13:28,160 --> 02:13:29,920
Your brother still thinks we are together.

1461
02:13:32,520 --> 02:13:33,640
Did he block your way again?

1462
02:13:35,800 --> 02:13:38,080
He probably does not believe
it because we still talk.

1463
02:13:38,520 --> 02:13:40,320
I will tell him it is no longer necessary.

1464
02:13:42,120 --> 02:13:43,280
Why are you down?

1465
02:13:45,600 --> 02:13:46,600
My mind is on Mercan.

1466
02:13:47,440 --> 02:13:50,600
She is devastated after
everything that happened.

1467
02:13:52,080 --> 02:13:54,480
And all I can do is talk.

1468
02:13:56,960 --> 02:13:59,440
I truly do not know what to do for her.

1469
02:14:01,200 --> 02:14:02,960
What happened upset me too.

1470
02:14:05,520 --> 02:14:07,039
We also started a nice relationship.

1471
02:14:07,040 --> 02:14:10,120
Once trust is broken,
it is hard to rebuild.

1472
02:14:11,440 --> 02:14:15,320
Look, we both understood it would not work.

1473
02:14:16,080 --> 02:14:17,080
Demet.

1474
02:14:17,360 --> 02:14:19,200
Would you reconsider?

1475
02:14:20,320 --> 02:14:21,720
No need, Burak.

1476
02:14:22,680 --> 02:14:25,360
Look, we stayed friends.

1477
02:14:28,040 --> 02:14:29,440
Let it stay this way.

1478
02:14:30,960 --> 02:14:32,040
Do not expect more.

1479
02:14:35,560 --> 02:14:36,560
All right.

1480
02:14:53,400 --> 02:14:56,080
Mashallah. Did you make soup for me?

1481
02:14:56,440 --> 02:14:58,320
Enjoy, my husband.

1482
02:15:00,080 --> 02:15:01,320
I am tasting it right away.

1483
02:15:06,240 --> 02:15:07,440
How is it?

1484
02:15:09,400 --> 02:15:11,080
Let me tell you something.

1485
02:15:12,280 --> 02:15:14,760
This soup is perfect. Bless your hands.

1486
02:15:15,240 --> 02:15:16,280
Enjoy it, my husband.

1487
02:15:18,920 --> 02:15:20,160
May it heal you.

1488
02:15:23,000 --> 02:15:24,000
Berat.

1489
02:15:25,160 --> 02:15:27,400
We got married, but I am not at peace.

1490
02:15:29,600 --> 02:15:30,600
What happened?

1491
02:15:33,400 --> 02:15:37,440
Your mother does not
want me, and she shows it.

1492
02:15:39,360 --> 02:15:41,680
Can someone be happy
where they are not wanted?

1493
02:15:42,440 --> 02:15:45,800
It is new, my dear. She is adjusting.

1494
02:15:45,920 --> 02:15:47,440
It will get better. Do not worry.

1495
02:15:50,840 --> 02:15:52,920
Would you talk to her again?

1496
02:15:54,120 --> 02:15:56,879
All right. I will talk. Let
them come. I will handle it.

1497
02:15:56,880 --> 02:15:57,880
Do not worry.
Okay.

1498
02:16:00,240 --> 02:16:03,160
Let me say something.
The soup is really good.

1499
02:16:08,480 --> 02:16:10,400
Welcome, Çiçek.

1500
02:16:12,800 --> 02:16:14,240
Your sister in law made soup.

1501
02:16:15,120 --> 02:16:16,120
Drink it. Do not miss it.

1502
02:16:18,840 --> 02:16:20,000
No, thanks.

1503
02:16:20,880 --> 02:16:21,880
Drink it.

1504
02:16:23,360 --> 02:16:24,560
I said no.

1505
02:16:36,520 --> 02:16:37,520
Mom.

1506
02:16:38,760 --> 02:16:40,360
My dear mom.

1507
02:16:41,960 --> 02:16:42,960
My precious.

1508
02:16:43,560 --> 02:16:45,320
Look at this.

1509
02:16:45,560 --> 02:16:46,560
How are you, mom?

1510
02:16:51,120 --> 02:16:53,160
I am fine, my son.

1511
02:16:55,080 --> 02:16:56,960
Shall we talk, mom?

1512
02:16:59,880 --> 02:17:02,360
What will you talk
about? I have things to do.

1513
02:17:03,560 --> 02:17:08,160
Mom, what if you gave up this stubbornness?

1514
02:17:08,840 --> 02:17:10,840
Look, Zehra and I…

1515
02:17:12,560 --> 02:17:14,080
started a path together.

1516
02:17:15,400 --> 02:17:17,680
We signed, we exchanged rings.

1517
02:17:17,800 --> 02:17:19,800
She is your daughter in law now.

1518
02:17:20,200 --> 02:17:21,200
Right?

1519
02:17:28,280 --> 02:17:29,280
Is that not right?

1520
02:17:29,640 --> 02:17:30,640
Is it not?

1521
02:17:31,960 --> 02:17:33,120
Let me kiss your hand, mom.

1522
02:17:44,200 --> 02:17:48,920
Mom, look, you are upset and we are upset.

1523
02:17:50,280 --> 02:17:51,560
What if this coldness ended?

1524
02:17:52,840 --> 02:17:54,760
Would it not be better if everyone smiled?

1525
02:17:55,200 --> 02:17:56,600
Right, Çiçek?

1526
02:17:58,440 --> 02:18:00,000
Come on, mom. Be generous.

1527
02:18:02,120 --> 02:18:03,680
Show us your grace.

1528
02:18:09,960 --> 02:18:11,680
Look, I am sad.

1529
02:18:14,920 --> 02:18:16,720
Come on, let me kiss your hand.

1530
02:18:17,400 --> 02:18:18,480
Mom.

1531
02:18:19,000 --> 02:18:20,000
My dear mom.

1532
02:18:20,120 --> 02:18:22,400
You did it again. You showed your grace.

1533
02:18:23,280 --> 02:18:24,360
Kiss grandma’s hand.

1534
02:18:24,840 --> 02:18:25,840
Let me kiss it.

1535
02:18:29,920 --> 02:18:31,160
My dear mom.

1536
02:18:31,640 --> 02:18:33,200
See, she showed her grace again.

1537
02:18:36,880 --> 02:18:38,760
I will take the plates to the table.

1538
02:18:39,680 --> 02:18:40,680
Then I will…

1539
02:18:41,440 --> 02:18:42,760
take these too.

1540
02:18:44,480 --> 02:18:46,880
Brother, are you doing chores?

1541
02:18:47,280 --> 02:18:49,000
My eyes filled with tears.

1542
02:18:50,040 --> 02:18:51,936
What will happen? I can do
it. My hands will not fall off.

1543
02:18:51,960 --> 02:18:53,560
You will lose strength.

1544
02:18:53,920 --> 02:18:54,920
Çiçek.

1545
02:18:55,200 --> 02:18:55,880
Nothing will happen.

1546
02:18:56,200 --> 02:18:57,280
Çiçek, nothing will happen.

1547
02:18:57,480 --> 02:18:58,480
I always do it.

1548
02:19:00,160 --> 02:19:02,720
Son, what are you letting them do to you?

1549
02:19:03,640 --> 02:19:04,760
God forbid.

1550
02:19:06,680 --> 02:19:09,480
Mom, I guess you approved Zehra
since you let her kiss your hand.

1551
02:19:10,640 --> 02:19:12,200
Look at me.

1552
02:19:13,480 --> 02:19:14,480
Look.

1553
02:19:14,520 --> 02:19:14,960
Did you see?

1554
02:19:15,080 --> 02:19:16,080
Do I have that look?

1555
02:19:17,360 --> 02:19:19,280
Mrs. Binnaz, did you play a trick?

1556
02:19:19,640 --> 02:19:21,360
We must have played a trick.

1557
02:19:22,120 --> 02:19:23,960
The hand is strong or
the gentleman is strong.

1558
02:19:24,200 --> 02:19:25,880
We will see, Ms. Zehra.

1559
02:20:25,760 --> 02:20:27,440
I never wanted you to go through all this.

1560
02:20:42,520 --> 02:20:43,760
My heart lost control.

1561
02:20:48,320 --> 02:20:49,720
I could not handle you.

1562
02:20:51,120 --> 02:20:52,520
You captured me.

1563
02:20:54,840 --> 02:21:02,840
Your hair, your eyes, your
face, your smile, your heart.

1564
02:21:04,840 --> 02:21:07,600
I fell in love with every part of you.

1565
02:21:50,320 --> 02:21:51,760
We can go now.

1566
02:21:57,400 --> 02:21:58,920
I know you are angry at me.

1567
02:22:00,320 --> 02:22:01,920
But in the end, you will forgive me.

1568
02:22:04,520 --> 02:22:06,880
Your confidence is admirable.

1569
02:22:08,120 --> 02:22:10,400
But do not trust it so much.

1570
02:22:11,720 --> 02:22:13,000
I trust our love.

1571
02:22:14,000 --> 02:22:16,840
You told me so many lies.

1572
02:22:17,560 --> 02:22:19,760
Now you talk about the
past, love, forgiveness.

1573
02:22:22,000 --> 02:22:24,240
You became fire and burned everything.

1574
02:22:26,480 --> 02:22:29,240
You gave up on Tahir and
filled yourself with revenge.

1575
02:22:31,760 --> 02:22:34,040
You told me Tahir was dead.

1576
02:22:34,840 --> 02:22:37,680
I read his death in a
fake newspaper clipping.

1577
02:22:39,480 --> 02:22:43,000
Did you never think about how I felt?

1578
02:22:45,160 --> 02:22:48,120
I could not even rejoice that
Tahir was alive because of you.

1579
02:22:50,120 --> 02:22:51,560
It might be because Tahir is me.

1580
02:22:55,400 --> 02:22:57,920
You are annoyed with me
these days for that reason.

1581
02:23:09,320 --> 02:23:10,840
Mercan, what are you doing?

1582
02:23:12,040 --> 02:23:13,080
I am taking revenge.

1583
02:23:15,200 --> 02:23:16,800
You know revenge well.

1584
02:23:18,600 --> 02:23:19,600
I am telling you to stop.

1585
02:23:23,080 --> 02:23:24,560
Stop. Do not resist.

1586
02:23:27,080 --> 02:23:29,240
I will not let you run away anymore.

1587
02:23:31,840 --> 02:23:32,840
I will not give up.

1588
02:23:34,640 --> 02:23:35,640
I will not surrender.

1589
02:23:37,320 --> 02:23:39,080
You already gave up on me.

1590
02:23:39,680 --> 02:23:41,720
I never truly existed for you anyway.

1591
02:23:42,760 --> 02:23:43,880
You know that is not true.

1592
02:23:44,000 --> 02:23:45,000
I do not know.

1593
02:23:45,600 --> 02:23:48,240
All I know is you took
your revenge successfully.

1594
02:23:49,960 --> 02:23:51,440
When the time is up, we will divorce.

1595
02:23:54,160 --> 02:23:56,400
The only thing that
matters to you is revenge.

1596
02:23:56,640 --> 02:23:58,000
That is the only truth for you.

1597
02:23:58,400 --> 02:24:00,280
My revenge is as big as my love.

1598
02:24:01,720 --> 02:24:02,720
And just as real.

1599
02:24:10,520 --> 02:24:11,720
As big as your revenge?

1600
02:24:12,000 --> 02:24:13,000
Yes.

1601
02:24:15,120 --> 02:24:16,120
All right.

1602
02:24:17,520 --> 02:24:18,520
Then so be it.

1603
02:24:20,240 --> 02:24:23,960
If your love is as real
and as big as your revenge…

1604
02:24:25,920 --> 02:24:27,840
if you had to choose between them,

1605
02:24:29,560 --> 02:24:32,440
could you give up your
revenge for your love?
